(116, 'DÃ¢y Chuyá»n NÆ°á»›c Ngá»t ÄÃ³ng Chai Táº¡i Vá»¥ Báº£n Nam Äá»‹nh', NULL, NULL, '', '{"detail":"<h1 class=\\"h3\\" style=\\"font-size: 24px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\">D\\u00e2y chuy\\u1ec1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ecdt \\u0111\\u00f3ng chai t\\u1ea1i V\\u1ee5 B\\u1ea3n Nam \\u0110\\u1ecbnh<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p class=\\"post-info\\" style=\\"color: #777777; font-size: 13px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\"><span class=\\"txt\\">03\\/03\\/2020 16:31<\\/span>\\u00a0<span class=\\"txt\\">|<\\/span>\\u00a0<span class=\\"share share-sm\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\"post-body\\" style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\">\\r\\n<p>D\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n d\\u00e2y chuy\\u1ec1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ecdt \\u0111\\u00f3ng chai\\u00a0 V\\u1ee5 B\\u1ea3n\\u00a0Nam \\u0110\\u1ecbnh nh\\u1eb1m cung c\\u1ea5p n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng tinh khi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u00f3ng chai cung c\\u1ea5p cho th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng khu v\\u1ef1c. \\u0110\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 v\\u1ec7 sinh an to\\u00e0n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-2.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"text-justify\\">N\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u00f3ng chai \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 u\\u1ed1ng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a kho\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 cacbon dioxit (CO2) t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ed5 sung nh\\u01b0ng kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kho\\u00e1ng thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u00f3ng chai v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ee9a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng, c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1o ng\\u1ecdt, c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1o h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 lo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m n\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1c. (Theo QCVN 6-1:21961196\\/BYT).<br \\/>Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u00f3ng chai c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea5y t\\u1eeb nhi\\u1ec1u ngu\\u1ed3n: N\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u00e1y th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u1eb7t, th\\u1eadm ch\\u00ed l\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc bi\\u1ec3n. Nh\\u01b0ng quan tr\\u1ecdng l\\u00e0 kh\\u00e2u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd \\u0111\\u1ea7u ngu\\u1ed3n sao cho gi\\u1ea3m t\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ecdng t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e1ng k\\u1ec3, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea9m \\u1ed5n \\u0111inh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-10.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-6.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-13.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-12.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/du-an-day-chuyen-nuoc-ngot-dong-chai-nam-dinh-gmc-3.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r