(119, 'Láº¯p Äáº·t Lá»c Tá»•ng TÃ²a NhÃ  Florence Má»¹ ÄÃ¬nh', NULL, NULL, '', '{"detail":"<h1 class=\\"h3\\" style=\\"font-size: 24px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\">L\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t L\\u1ecdc t\\u1ed5ng t\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Florence M\\u1ef9 \\u0110\\u00ecnh<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p class=\\"post-info\\" style=\\"color: #777777; font-size: 13px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\"><span class=\\"txt\\">27\\/02\\/2020 11:25<\\/span>\\u00a0<span class=\\"txt\\">|<\\/span>\\u00a0<span class=\\"share share-sm\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\"post-body\\" style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\">\\r\\n<p class=\\"text-justify\\">Florence M\\u1ef9 \\u0110\\u00ecnh\\u00a0t\\u1ecda l\\u1ea1c t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 v\\u00f4 c\\u00f9ng\\u00a0ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o s\\u1ed1 28 Tr\\u1ea7n H\\u1eefu D\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn ph\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n b\\u1eadc nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a M\\u1ef9 \\u0110\\u00ecnh, Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam, H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"text-justify\\">N\\u1eb1m c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng H\\u1ed3 T\\u00f9ng M\\u1eadu ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn 300m, v\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i c\\u00e1c tuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng giao th\\u00f4ng v\\u00f4 c\\u00f9ng quan tr\\u1ecdng: \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u00e0nh \\u0111ai 3, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng L\\u00ea \\u0110\\u1ee9c Th\\u1ecd n\\u00ean c\\u01b0 d\\u00e2n t\\u1ea1i X3 M\\u1ef9 \\u0110\\u00ecnh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady c\\u01b0 d\\u00e2n s\\u1ed1ng t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c khu v\\u1ef1c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kh\\u00e1c c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u00f4 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/florence-gmc-water.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 30px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong>Nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Florence M\\u1ef9 \\u0110\\u00ecnh y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ecdc t\\u1ed5ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ngu\\u1ed3n, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o nhu c\\u1ea7u n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea1ch, an to\\u00e0n\\u00a0cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 30px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong>Gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u00e1p \\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eefng y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u tr\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA ph\\u1ea3i ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t, t\\u00ednh to\\u00e1n \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p l\\u1ecdc t\\u1ed5ng ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n, ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 an to\\u00e0n cho s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti\\u00eau d\\u00f9ng khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sinh ho\\u1ea1t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong>K\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n sau thi c\\u00f4ng<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/b27a51b569db9185c8ca.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/83e588acb0c2489c11d3.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/c17de44490d4688a31c5.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 20px;\\"><strong><img class=\\"img-responsive center-block\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcvina.com\\/photo\\/762e2cf05960a13ef871.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>MST: 0107998239 do S\\u1edf K\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i c\\u1ea5p ng\\u00e0y 20\\/09\\/2017<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh: S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>VPGD: T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>VPGD chi nh\\u00e1nh TP. HCM\\u00a0: s\\u1ed1\\u00a092\\/20B\\/20\\/17 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Ph\\u1ea1m H\\u00f9ng, Ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng 4, Qu\\u1eadn 8, TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"tel:02466 835383\\">02466 835383<\\/a>\\u00a0- \\u00a0Fax:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"tel:02466.835383\\">02466.835383<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Hotline: 0989980178<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Email:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"mailto:info@gmcvina.com\\">info@gmcvina.com<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>","specification":"","media":"<p><iframe src=\\"\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/X3CLCILkrUA\\" width=\\"625\\" height=\\"516\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>"}', 'Láº¯p Äáº·t Lá»c Tá»•ng TÃ²a NhÃ  Florence Má»¹ ÄÃ¬nh', 'Láº¯p Äáº·t Lá»c Tá»•ng TÃ²a NhÃ  Florence Má»¹ ÄÃ¬nh', 'Láº¯p Äáº·t Lá»c 