cho s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng theo quy chu\\u1ea9n QCVN:2009\\/BYT c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 Y T\\u1ebf ban h\\u00e0nh. H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1ea1i M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan\\u2026chi ph\\u00ed b\\u1ea3o d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng th\\u1ea5p, c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng thu h\\u1ed3i v\\u1ed1n nhanh, mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf c\\u1ea1nh tranh m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c doanh nghi\\u1ec7p trong c\\u00f9ng ng\\u00e0nh n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Mui%20Hoi\\/He%20thong%20xu%20ly%20nuoc%20co%20mui%20hoi%20(3).jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"719\\" height=\\"479\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. GI\\u1ea2I PH\\u00c1P X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC C\\u00d3 M\\u00d9I H\\u00d4I<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">1. V\\u00ec sao n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan ho\\u1eb7c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u1eb7t khi cung c\\u1ea5p cho s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 do trong ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea5p ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n ch\\u1ea5t th\\u1ea3i, ch\\u1ea5t h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc m\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 l\\u1ecdc, b\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0N\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i tanh kh\\u00f3 m\\u00e0 nh\\u1ea7m l\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c so v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00e1c. Ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u khi b\\u01a1m l\\u00ean, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00e1 trong, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u00f3 k\\u1ebft t\\u1ee7a s\\u1eaft m\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, trong ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m c\\u00f2n ch\\u1ee9a h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng nh\\u01b0 Asen, ch\\u00ec, mangan,\\u2026,\\u00a0 kh\\u00ed CO2, v\\u00e0 kh\\u00ed H2S n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 cao c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y ra m\\u00f9i l\\u1ea1 nh\\u01b0 m\\u00f9i tr\\u1ee9ng th\\u1ed1i trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc nh\\u01b0 thu\\u1ed1c b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 th\\u1ef1c v\\u1eadt, h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t, ch\\u1ea5t th\\u1ea3i t\\u1eeb d\\u00f2ng ch\\u1ea3y m\\u1eb7t l\\u1eafng xu\\u1ed1ng g\\u00e2y m\\u00f9i l\\u1ea1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Trong ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u1eb7t, s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ed1 r\\u00f2 r\\u1ec9 ch\\u1ea5t th\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0o b\\u00ean trong ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ea5p nh\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec5m d\\u1ea7u, nhi\\u1ec5m b\\u00f9n th\\u1ea3i d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i r\\u1ea5t kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0M\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i trong ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eefng g\\u00e2y c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i trong s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, m\\u1ea5t m\\u00f9i v\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0103n, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng, m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1edbi s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi, c\\u00f3 nguy c\\u01a1 ti\\u1ec1m \\u1ea9n c\\u00e1c b\\u1ec7nh ti\\u00eau h\\u00f3a, vi\\u00eam da, d\\u1ecb \\u1ee9ng,\\u2026 \\u0110\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3m thi\\u1ec3u, ho\\u1eb7c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n t\\u00e1c h\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang c\\u1ea7n t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u c\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7n ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf nguy\\u00ean nh\\u00e2n g\\u00e2y m\\u00f9i b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7n ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd h\\u00f3a sinh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 2. C\\u00e1ch x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Khi trong ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i b\\u1ea1n n\\u00ean d\\u1eebng l\\u1ea1i m\\u1ecdi ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0103n u\\u1ed1ng, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho sinh ho\\u1ea1t b\\u1eb1ng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nguy\\u00ean nh\\u00e2n x\\u1eed l\\u00fd k\\u1ecbp th\\u1eddi. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i nh\\u01b0:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 M\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e1ch v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c h\\u1ed9 gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng l\\u00e0 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng b\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc c\\u00e1t k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi gi\\u00e0n phun m\\u01b0a (trong tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u1ee9a h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1eaft cao). C\\u1ee9 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1edbp c\\u00e1t l\\u1ea1i k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi 1 l\\u1edbp than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh, l\\u1eb7p l\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi \\u0111\\u1ea7y b\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc. Than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1eb7c t\\u00ednh h\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5 cao s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf m\\u00e0u, v\\u00e0 m\\u00f9i l\\u1ea1 c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\\u00ean c\\u0169ng c\\u1ea7n ch\\u00fa \\u00fd, th\\u1eddi gian s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh c\\u00f3 h\\u1ea1n, khi \\u0111\\u00e3 h\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u1ea7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m, c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i thay th\\u1ebf b\\u1eb1ng than m\\u1edbi.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Mui%20Hoi\\/Quy%20trinh%20xu%20ly%20nuoc%20co%20mui%20hoi.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"418\\" height=\\"400\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"attachment_4050\\" class=\\"wp-caption alignnone\\" style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-size: 14px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\"><br \\/>\\r\\n<p class=\\"wp-caption-text\\" style=\\"font-size: 16px;\\">X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i b\\u1eb1ng gi\\u00e0n phun m\\u01b0a<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 Oxy h\\u00f3a: s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t nh\\u01b0 Clo, kali permanganate, ozone \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf m\\u00f9i, v\\u1ecb. Clo c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf m\\u00f9i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 s\\u1eaft, mangan. Kali permaganat th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u1eed c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 trong khi Chlorine dioxide \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 phenol, t\\u1ea3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 C\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 x\\u1ea3y ra tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p b\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee9a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i do b\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee9a t\\u1eeb r\\u1ea5t l\\u00e2u ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thau r\\u1eeda, g\\u00e2y ra t\\u00edch t\\u1ee5 c\\u1eb7n b\\u1ea9n, r\\u00eau m\\u1ed1c, ho\\u1eb7c x\\u00e1c c\\u00f4n tr\\u00f9ng, \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1eadt b\\u1ecb r\\u01a1i v\\u00e0o b\\u1ec3 m\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u00fa \\u00fd. L\\u00fac n\\u00e0y c\\u1ea7n x\\u1ea3 h\\u1ebft\\u00a0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong b\\u1ec3, c\\u1ecd r\\u1eeda, lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf b\\u1ee5i b\\u1ea9n trong b\\u1ec3.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>3. H\\u00ccNH \\u1ea2NH &amp; VIDEO.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span>\\u00a0<img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Mui%20Hoi\\/He%20thong%20xu%20ly%20nuoc%20co%20mui%20hoi%20(3).jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"700\\" height=\\"466\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span><img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Mui%20Hoi\\/He%20thong%20xu%20ly%20nuoc%20co%20mui%20hoi%20(2).jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"395\\" height=\\"527\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span><img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Mui%20Hoi\\/He%20thong%20xu%20ly%20nuoc%20co%20mui%20hoi%20(1).jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"395\\" height=\\"527\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>4. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG N\\u1ed4I B\\u1eacT.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1eeb\\u00a0M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 C\\u00f3 thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ng\\u1eaft m\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u00e1y ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh khi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n \\u00e1p l\\u00ean xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 V\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ecbu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft kh\\u1eafc nghi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n cho thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nh\\u1ecf g\\u1ecdn, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, t\\u1ed1n \\u00edt di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>5. \\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u00a0H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng d\\u00f9ng trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f4ng,n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc\\u00a0c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i\\u00a0tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sinh ho\\u1ea1t chung.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>6. QUY TR\\u00ccNH D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 L\\u1eaeP \\u0110\\u1eb6T H\\u1ec6 TH\\u1ed0NG\\u00a0X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC C\\u00d3 M\\u00d9I H\\u00d4I T\\u1ea0I GMC VINA.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1: Ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA\\u00a0Ho\\u1eb7c g\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i qua Hotline:\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 2: Kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf (Ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u00e0, c\\u00f4ng ty, c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra, kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 3: T\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p b\\u00e1o gi\\u00e1 d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt t\\u01b0.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 4: K\\u00fd h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh thi c\\u00f4ng (Nhanh ch\\u00f3ng k\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3 ngo\\u00e0i gi\\u1edd h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh, th\\u1ee9 7 v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eadt)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 5: B\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>7. L\\u00dd DO B\\u1ea0N N\\u00caN CH\\u1eccN GMC VINA KH\\u00d4NG PH\\u1ea2I L\\u00c0 \\u0110\\u01a0N V\\u1eca N\\u00c0O KH\\u00c1C<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb chuy\\u00ean v\\u1ec1 x\\u01b0 l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0quy m\\u00f4 l\\u1edbn, nh\\u1ecf\\u00a0v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 s\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Am hi\\u1ec3u s\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7c th\\u00f9 y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd t\\u1eebng l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Chuy\\u00ean x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1eefng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00f3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p, \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec1u khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ecba h\\u00ecnh kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao t\\u1eeb M\\u1ef9, EU.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">B\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh h\\u1eadu m\\u00e3i nhanh ch\\u00f3ng b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec tr\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1eddi.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay v\\u1edbi\\u00a0C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA\\u00a0h\\u00f4m nay \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i chuy\\u00ean\\u00a0thi c\\u00f4ng, l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t, b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u00e1y c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i, m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n b\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc t\\u1ed1n di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch, v\\u1eabn\\u00a0 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o x\\u1eed l\\u00fd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea1ch, \\u0111\\u1ea1t y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng sinh ho\\u1ea1t, an to\\u00e0n cho s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng theo quy chu\\u1ea9n QCVN:2009\\/BYT c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 Y T\\u1ebf ban h\\u00e0nh. Trong h\\u01a1n 16 n\\u0103m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i lu\\u00f4n nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 tin t\\u01b0\\u1edfng tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u1eeb ph\\u00eda kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 quy tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p, gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea3 h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd. C\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi van \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n, van r\\u1eeda ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c, \\u2026 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m th\\u1eddi gian v\\u1ec7 sinh h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng. Ngo\\u00e0i vi\\u1ec7c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf m\\u00f9i h\\u00f4i trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u00fap l\\u1ecdc s\\u1ea1ch c\\u00e1c kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng kh\\u00f4ng t\\u1ed1t nh\\u01b0 mangan, s\\u1eaft, ch\\u00ec,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp; C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh:\\u00a0<\\/strong>S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>VPGD:\\u00a0<\\/strong>T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>\\u0110i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i:\\u00a0<\\/strong>02466 835383 - \\u00a0Fax: 02466.835383<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Hotline:<\\/strong>\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Website:\\u00a0<\\/strong><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcwater.com\\/\\"><span>https:\\/\\/gmcwater.com\\/<\\/span><\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","specification":"","media":""}', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c CÃ³ MÃ¹i HÃ´i', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c CÃ³ MÃ¹i HÃ´i', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c CÃ³ MÃ¹i HÃ´i', 0, 63, 2, '2020-03-19 03:50:04', '2020-03-19 03:50:04'),
(128, 'CÃ´ng nghá»‡ xá»­ lÃ½ nÆ°á»›c tháº£i Biochip MBBR (Moving Bed Bio Reactor)', NULL, NULL, '', '{"detail":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">GMC VINA- \\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m\\u00a0kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong vi\\u1ec7c nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3 ph\\u1ea9m v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i Biochip MBBR (Moving Bed Bio \\u0111\\u00e3 ch\\u1ee9ng minh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 uy t\\u00edn, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch cho ra \\u0111\\u1eddi nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 v\\u00e0o vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, gi\\u1ea3m thi\\u1ec3u \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">I.\\u00a0 GI\\u1edaI THI\\u1ec6U V\\u1ec0 C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC TH\\u1ea2I\\u00a0 BIOCHIP \\u00a0MBBR (MOVING BED BIO REACTOR)<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i MBBR (Moving bed bioreactor): L\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng k\\u0129 thu\\u1eadt vi sinh d\\u00ednh b\\u00e1m tr\\u00ean l\\u1edbp v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u mang di chuy\\u1ec3n. Do d\\u00f9ng v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u mang vi sinh n\\u00ean m\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ed9 vi sinh (MLVSS) trong b\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd cao h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi k\\u0129 thu\\u1eadt b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh ph\\u00e2n t\\u00e1n. C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 l\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p gi\\u1eefa Aerotank truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng v\\u00e0 l\\u1ecdc sinh h\\u1ecdc hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 MBBR ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd cao. V\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u00e0m gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u1ea3i c\\u00f3 t\\u1ef7 tr\\u1ecdng nh\\u1eb9 h\\u01a1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c. C\\u00e1c gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 n\\u00e0y lu\\u00f4n chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng kh\\u00f4ng ng\\u1eebng trong to\\u00e0n th\\u1ec3 t\\u00edch b\\u1ec3 nh\\u1edd c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb th\\u1ed5i kh\\u00ed v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1nh khu\\u1ea5y. M\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ed9 vi sinh ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng gia t\\u0103ng, hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng cao.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 18pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\">II. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG N\\u1ed4I B\\u1eacT\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\">C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC TH\\u1ea2I\\u00a0 BIOCHIP \\u00a0MBBR (MOVING BED BIO REACTOR)<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">N\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i t\\u1eeb b\\u1ec3 thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed t\\u1ef1 ch\\u1ea3y qua b\\u1ec3 MBBR d\\u00f9ng gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 biochip \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n x\\u1eed l\\u00fd hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed. B\\u1ec3 MBBR \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed v\\u1edbi l\\u1edbp m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc di \\u0111\\u1ed9ng. Trong b\\u1ec3 MBBR, m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n tr\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng trong h\\u1ed7n d\\u1ecbch c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ec3 ph\\u1ea3n \\u1ee9ng, qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh th\\u1ed5i kh\\u00ed l\\u00e0m c\\u00e1c gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 vi sinh chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng. Song ch\\u1eafn (gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 r\\u00e2y) gi\\u1eef c\\u00e1c gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 vi sinh kh\\u00f4ng ra kh\\u1ecfi b\\u1ec3.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Thai\\/Cong%20Nghe%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Thai\\/Cong%20Nghe%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20thai%20Biochip%20MBBR\\/Cong-%20Nghe-Xu-ly-%20nuoc-thai-%20Biochip%20MBBR-gmc-water-3.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"750\\" height=\\"373\\" \\/><br \\/> <br \\/>Trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n, m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc b\\u1ecb \\u201cb\\u00f3c\\u201d ra kh\\u1ecfi gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap duy tr\\u00ec \\u0111\\u1ed9 d\\u00e0y th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p cho m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc theo t\\u1ea3i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u v\\u00e0o. Sinh kh\\u1ed1i d\\u01b0 b\\u1ecb b\\u00f3c s\\u1ebd \\u0111i qua song ch\\u1eafn ra ngo\\u00e0i. B\\u1ec3 l\\u1eafng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf sinh kh\\u1ed1i d\\u01b0 ra kh\\u1ecfi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i sau x\\u1eed l\\u00fd. C\\u00e1c gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o t\\u1eeb poyethylene t\\u1ef7 tr\\u1ecdng cao, tr\\u1ecdng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ri\\u00eang l\\u00e0 0.95-0.98.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 MBBR l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi nh\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n nay trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i v\\u00ec ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd cao v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c \\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t tr\\u1ed9i:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">H\\u1ec7 vi sinh b\\u1ec1n: c\\u00e1c gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 vi sinh t\\u1ea1o cho m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc m\\u1ed9t m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7, do \\u0111\\u00f3, h\\u1ec7 vi sinh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd d\\u1ec5 ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">M\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ed9 vi sinh cao: so v\\u1edbi b\\u1ec3 th\\u1ed5i kh\\u00ed th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng, m\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ed9 vi sinh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong m\\u1ed7i \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb th\\u1ec3 t\\u00edch cao h\\u01a1n, do \\u0111\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u00edch b\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1ecf h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 cao h\\u01a1n.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ch\\u1ee7ng vi sinh \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng: c\\u00e1c nh\\u00f3m vi sinh kh\\u00e1c nhau ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp m\\u00e0ng vi sinh, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap cho c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n theo xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1eadp trung v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 chuy\\u00ean bi\\u1ec7t.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">D\\u1ec5 v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh, d\\u00ea\\u0303 da\\u0300ng n\\u00e2ng c\\u00e2\\u0301p.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">T\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ecdng cao, bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m l\\u1edbn: kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a m\\u00e0ng sinh h\\u1ecdc theo t\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ecdng t\\u0103ng d\\u1ea7n c\\u1ee7a ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 l\\u00e0m cho b\\u1ec3 MBBR c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh \\u1edf t\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ecdng cao v\\u00e0 bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng l\\u1edbn. Hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t x\\u1eed l\\u00fd BOD l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ebfn 90%.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">D\\u00ea\\u0303 ki\\u00ea\\u0309m soa\\u0301t h\\u00ea\\u0323 th\\u00f4\\u0301ng: co\\u0301 th\\u00ea\\u0309 b\\u00f4\\u0309 sung gia\\u0301 th\\u00ea\\u0309 Biofilm t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u01b0\\u0301ng v\\u01a1\\u0301i ta\\u0309i tro\\u0323ng \\u00f4 nhi\\u00ea\\u0303m va\\u0300 l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0323ng n\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0301c tha\\u0309i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ti\\u00ea\\u0301t ki\\u00ea\\u0323m di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch: gi\\u1ea3m 30-40% th\\u00ea\\u0309 ti\\u0301ch b\\u00ea\\u0309 so v\\u01a1\\u0301i c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u00ea\\u0323 bu\\u0300n hoa\\u0323t ti\\u0301nh l\\u01a1 l\\u01b0\\u0309ng v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd kh\\u00e1c.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng cho h\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i c\\u00f3 \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1: N\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i sinh ho\\u1ea1t, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i y t\\u1ebf, th\\u1ee7y h\\u1ea3i s\\u1ea3n, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, d\\u1ec7t nhu\\u1ed9m\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\"><strong><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">III. TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"2\\" width=\\"775\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td width=\\"293\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><br \\/>Th\\u00f4ng s\\u1ed1 thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"225\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"257\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ng\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td width=\\"293\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Th\\u1eddi gian l\\u01b0u trong b\\u1ec3 Anoxic<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"225\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">h<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"257\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">1.0 \\u2013 1.2<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td width=\\"293\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Th\\u1eddi gian l\\u01b0u trong b\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"225\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">h<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"257\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">3.5 \\u2013 4.5<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td width=\\"293\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t l\\u1edbp biofilm<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"225\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">m2\\/m3<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"257\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">200 \\u2013 250<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td width=\\"293\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">T\\u1ea1i tr\\u1ecdng BOD<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"225\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Kg\\/m3.d<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td width=\\"257\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">1.0 \\u2013 1.4<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\">IV. L\\u00dd DO B\\u1ea0N N\\u00caN CH\\u1eccN GMC VINA KH\\u00d4NG PH\\u1ea2I L\\u00c0 \\u0110\\u01a0N V\\u1eca N\\u00c0O KH\\u00c1C<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Roboto;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb chuy\\u00ean v\\u1ec1 x\\u01b0 l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0quy m\\u00f4 l\\u1edbn, nh\\u1ecf\\u00a0v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 s\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Am hi\\u1ec3u s\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7c th\\u00f9 y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd t\\u1eebng l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica