\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 Y T\\u1ebf ban h\\u00e0nh. H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1ea1i M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan\\u2026chi ph\\u00ed b\\u1ea3o d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng th\\u1ea5p, c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng thu h\\u1ed3i v\\u1ed1n nhanh, mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf c\\u1ea1nh tranh m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c doanh nghi\\u1ec7p trong c\\u00f9ng ng\\u00e0nh n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img style=\\"undefined\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Nhiem%20Mangan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Nhiem-Mangan-.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"700\\" height=\\"700\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. GI\\u1ea2I PH\\u00c1P X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC NHI\\u1ec4M MANGAN<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a01. T\\u1ea1i sao c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan?<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Mangan l\\u00e0 nguy\\u00ean t\\u1ed1 kim lo\\u1ea1i\\u00a0ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y trong l\\u1edbp v\\u1ecf tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t. N\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea5m qua c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea7ng \\u0111\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e1, h\\u00f2a tan c\\u00e1c kho\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ee9a mangan v\\u00e0 gi\\u1eef ch\\u00fang trong dung d\\u1ecbch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. Trong c\\u00e1c gi\\u1ebfng s\\u00e2u, n\\u01a1i c\\u00f3 h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng oxy th\\u1ea5p, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u1ee9a mangan kh\\u00f4ng m\\u00e0u do Mn2+\\u00a0b\\u1ecb h\\u00f2a tan. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, khi ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed, mangan b\\u1ecb oxy h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u1eeb d\\u1ea1ng kh\\u00f4ng m\\u00e0u, h\\u00f2a tan sang d\\u1ea1ng r\\u1eafn, c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u \\u0111en.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Mangan \\u1edf h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ecf kh\\u00f4ng g\\u00e2y nguy hi\\u1ec3m nh\\u01b0ng g\\u00e2y ra nh\\u1eefng phi\\u1ec1n to\\u00e1i trong vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00f3, n\\u1ebfu n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 mangan cao m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y ra c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe nghi\\u00eam tr\\u1ecdng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 trong s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><em style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0S\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe<\\/em><\\/strong>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Mangan l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ch\\u1ea5t dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu, c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft trong ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0103n u\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e0nh m\\u1ea1nh v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y trong th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m c\\u00f3 ngu\\u1ed3n g\\u1ed1c th\\u1ef1c v\\u1eadt nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i h\\u1ea1t, ng\\u0169 c\\u1ed1c v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eadu.\\u00a0C\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea7n m\\u1ed9t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng mangan \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u1ecfe m\\u1ea1nh, t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t \\u1edf h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng d\\u01b0\\u1edbi 0.1 mg\\/l.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng\\u00a0Mn2+\\u00a0l\\u1edbn h\\u01a1n 0.15 mg\\/l c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y ra nh\\u1eefng nguy h\\u1ea1i cho con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi, do u\\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong th\\u1eddi gian d\\u00e0i t\\u00edch t\\u1ee5 l\\u1ea1i trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3.\\u00a0T\\u00edch t\\u1ee5 mangan g\\u00e2y h\\u1ea1i cho h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ea7n kinh, t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee9ng c\\u00f3 t\\u00ean l\\u00e0 Manganism v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec3u hi\\u1ec7n run c\\u01a1 v\\u00e0 c\\u1ee9ng c\\u01a1, \\u0111i l\\u1ea1i kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n, n\\u00f3i k\\u00e9m v\\u00e0 k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng gi\\u1ea3m. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, \\u0111\\u1ed9c t\\u00ednh mangan c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra c\\u00e1c tri\\u1ec7u ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u01b0 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00e2m tr\\u1ea1ng, m\\u1ea5t tr\\u00ed nh\\u1edb ng\\u1eafn h\\u1ea1n, gi\\u1ea3m t\\u1eadp trung. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi cao tu\\u1ed5i v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ebb nh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t d\\u1ec5 b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m \\u0111\\u1ed9c mangan. V\\u1edbi tr\\u1ebb em do c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y mangan d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng nh\\u01b0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u1edbn, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi b\\u00e0i ti\\u1ebft \\u00edt h\\u01a1n, n\\u00ean n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 mangan t\\u00edch t\\u1ee5 l\\u1ea1i trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0L\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ti\\u00eau th\\u1ee5 h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y cho mangan ph\\u1ee5 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ed9 tu\\u1ed5i v\\u00e0 gi\\u1edbi t\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi. Theo WHO, l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng Mangan cho ph\\u00e9p t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u00e0o c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u00e0 0.4mg\\/l.\\u00a0\\u1ede Vi\\u1ec7t Nam theo QCVN 01: 2009\\/BYT th\\u00ec n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a cho ph\\u00e9p c\\u1ee7a Mn trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc l\\u00e0 0.3 mg\\/l. Tr\\u1ebb em v\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi gi\\u00e0 n\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 m\\u1ed9t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ecf h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u1ed9 tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f2n tr\\u1ebb. H\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao t\\u1eeb 1 \\u2013 5 mg\\/l g\\u00e2y ra kh\\u00f4ng \\u00edt \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1edbi c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp v\\u00e0 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><em style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Sinh ho\\u1ea1t, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Mangan trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m \\u1ed1 v\\u00e0ng qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o khi gi\\u1eb7t, g\\u00e2y ra c\\u00e1c m\\u1ea3ng b\\u00e1m tr\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, l\\u00e0m h\\u01b0 h\\u1ea1i, t\\u1eafc ngh\\u1ebdn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u1ed1ng; Mangan c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp c\\u1eb7n m\\u00e0u n\\u00e2u \\u0111en ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111en \\u0111\\u00f3ng b\\u00e1m tr\\u00ean nh\\u00e0 v\\u1ec7 sinh, v\\u00f2i hoa sen, b\\u1ed3n t\\u1eafm ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ed3n r\\u1eeda c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. H\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc v\\u00e0 m\\u00f9i v\\u1ecb thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m v\\u1ecb ngon \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0103n trong n\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbng c\\u1ee7a gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh b\\u1ea1n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0V\\u00ec v\\u1eady, vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan v\\u1eeba l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh, v\\u1eeba gi\\u00fap ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng, b\\u01a1m, x\\u1eed l\\u00fd, v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u1ed1ng v\\u1eadn chuy\\u1ec3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 2. C\\u00e1ch x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m mangan trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u1ede quy m\\u00f4 doanh nghi\\u1ec7p hay d\\u00e2n d\\u1ee5ng To\\u00e0n \\u00c1 \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 cung c\\u1ea5p cho b\\u1ea1n nh\\u1eefng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m mangan ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p, v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p \\u0111i\\u1ec3n h\\u00ecnh nh\\u01b0:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 L\\u00e0m m\\u1ec1m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc b\\u1eb1ng h\\u1ea1t ion: C\\u00e1c h\\u1ea1t ion mang \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thay th\\u1ebf ion Mn2+, gi\\u00fap lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n mangan, \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd mangan trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 \\u00c1p d\\u1ee5ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc RO: s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 th\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea5u ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn, cho ph\\u00e9p n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111i qua v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t r\\u1eafn h\\u00f2a tan. M\\u00e0ng RO c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf t\\u1edbi 99% mu\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u00f2a tan.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 Oxy h\\u00f3a mangan: Mangan l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ch\\u1ea5t d\\u1ec5 b\\u1ecb oxy h\\u00f3a, qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i Mn2+\\u00a0h\\u00f2a tan th\\u00e0nh d\\u1ea1ng kh\\u00f4ng h\\u00f2a tan, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf ra ngo\\u00e0i b\\u1eb1ng l\\u1ecdc \\u00e1p l\\u1ef1c ho\\u1eb7c l\\u1ecdc tr\\u1ecdng l\\u1ef1c. C\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t oxy h\\u00f3a h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ng\\u00e0y nay l\\u00e0 kali permanganat, clo v\\u00e0 ozone.\\u00a0 \\u0110\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n theo d\\u00f5i \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ea3 li\\u1ec1u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ch\\u1ea5t oxy h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc l\\u1ecdc th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p. Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c qua h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng l\\u1eafng l\\u1ecdc nh\\u01b0: than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh; c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 l\\u1ecdc m\\u00e0ng bao g\\u1ed3m vi l\\u1ecdc, si\\u00eau l\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 l\\u1ecdc nano.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 Keo t\\u1ee5 t\\u1ea1o b\\u00f4ng: l\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea1ng kh\\u00f4ng h\\u00f2a tan, lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf oxit kim lo\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf nh\\u1edd qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh l\\u1eafng v\\u00e0 l\\u1ecdc c\\u00e1c b\\u00f4ng c\\u1eb7n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0C\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u00e0y th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t v\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i \\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>3. H\\u00ccNH \\u1ea2NH &amp; VIDEO.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><img style=\\"undefined\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Nhiem%20Mangan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Nhiem-Mangan-.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"682\\" height=\\"682\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><img style=\\"undefined\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Nhiem%20Mangan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Nhiem-Mangan-2.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"596\\" height=\\"596\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>4. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG N\\u1ed4I B\\u1eacT.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1eeb\\u00a0M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 C\\u00f3 thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ng\\u1eaft m\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u00e1y ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh khi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n \\u00e1p l\\u00ean xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 V\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ecbu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft kh\\u1eafc nghi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n cho thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nh\\u1ecf g\\u1ecdn, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, t\\u1ed1n \\u00edt di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>5. \\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u00a0H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng d\\u00f9ng trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f4ng,n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc\\u00a0c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sinh ho\\u1ea1t chung.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>6. QUY TR\\u00ccNH D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 L\\u1eaeP \\u0110\\u1eb6T H\\u1ec6 TH\\u1ed0NG\\u00a0X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC NHI\\u1ec4M MANGAN T\\u1ea0I GMC VINA.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1: Ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA\\u00a0Ho\\u1eb7c g\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i qua Hotline:\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 2: Kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf (Ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u00e0, c\\u00f4ng ty, c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra, kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 3: T\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p b\\u00e1o gi\\u00e1 d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt t\\u01b0.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 4: K\\u00fd h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh thi c\\u00f4ng (Nhanh ch\\u00f3ng k\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3 ngo\\u00e0i gi\\u1edd h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh, th\\u1ee9 7 v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eadt)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 5: B\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>7. L\\u00dd DO B\\u1ea0N N\\u00caN CH\\u1eccN GMC VINA KH\\u00d4NG PH\\u1ea2I L\\u00c0 \\u0110\\u01a0N V\\u1eca N\\u00c0O KH\\u00c1C<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb chuy\\u00ean v\\u1ec1 x\\u01b0 l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0quy m\\u00f4 l\\u1edbn, nh\\u1ecf\\u00a0v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 s\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Am hi\\u1ec3u s\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7c th\\u00f9 y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd t\\u1eebng l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Chuy\\u00ean x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1eefng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00f3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p, \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec1u khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ecba h\\u00ecnh kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao t\\u1eeb M\\u1ef9, EU.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">B\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh h\\u1eadu m\\u00e3i nhanh ch\\u00f3ng b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec tr\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1eddi.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay v\\u1edbi\\u00a0C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA\\u00a0h\\u00f4m nay \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.\\u00a0\\u00a0GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean cung c\\u1ea5p h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan. \\u0110\\u1ec3 bi\\u1ebft ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 bao nhi\\u00eau, h\\u00e3y li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ty ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p, ph\\u1ee5 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o nhi\\u1ec1u y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 kh\\u00e1c nhau nh\\u01b0: n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 Mangan trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, s\\u1eaft, \\u0111\\u1ed9 ki\\u1ec1m, sunfua, amoniac v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 carbon h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 h\\u00f2a tan, c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p, kinh t\\u1ebf nh\\u1ea5t. Nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn, \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 v\\u00e0o h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng v\\u1edbi v\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u, chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh, h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t, x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ch\\u1ea5t th\\u1ea3i\\u2026 th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp; C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh:\\u00a0<\\/strong>S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>VPGD:\\u00a0<\\/strong>T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>\\u0110i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i:\\u00a0<\\/strong>02466 835383 - \\u00a0Fax: 02466.835383<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Hotline:<\\/strong>\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>Website:\\u00a0<\\/strong><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcwater.com\\/\\">https:\\/\\/gmcwater.com\\/<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","specification":"","media":""}', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Nhiá»…m Mangan', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Nhiá»…m Mangan', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Nhiá»…m Mangan', 0, 63, 2, '2020-03-19 04:36:35', '2020-03-19 04:36:35'),
(130, 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AFBR', NULL, NULL, '', '{"detail":"<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">M\\u1ed9t trong s\\u1ed1 nh\\u1eefng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c GMC VINA \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n hi\\u1ec7u xu\\u1ea5t, ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u0103ng ti\\u00eau th\\u1ee5 ph\\u1ea3i k\\u1ec3 t\\u1edbi AFBR. AFBR L\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n t\\u1eeb c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 FBR (Fixed Bed Reactor) \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ed5 sung h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng sensor c\\u1ea3m bi\\u1ebfn DO v\\u00e0 h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng kh\\u00ed g\\u00edup \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng oxi trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc lu\\u00f4n \\u1edf n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t tr\\u1ed9i \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u0103ng ti\\u00eau th\\u1ee5.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">I. GI\\u1edaI THI\\u1ec6U C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC TH\\u1ea2I\\u00a0AFBR<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec1n th\\u00e2n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 FBR (Fixed Bed Reactor), AFBR c\\u00f3 b\\u1ed5 sung h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng sensor \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ea3m bi\\u1ebfn DO c\\u00f9ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh ho\\u00e0n ch\\u1ec9nh k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o v\\u1edbi h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng kh\\u00ed t\\u1ea1o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ngu\\u1ed3n oxy gi\\u00fap n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc lu\\u00f4n \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh gi\\u00fap \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 FBR s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 h\\u00f2a tan (protein, tinh b\\u1ed9t,\\u2026), ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00f4 c\\u01a1 (nito, amoniac, photpho, d\\u1ea7u m\\u1ee1, b\\u00f9n c\\u00e1t, ch\\u1ea5t r\\u1eafn l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng, H2S,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\">II. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG\\u00a0C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC TH\\u1ea2I\\u00a0AFBR<\\/span>\\u00a0<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><em><strong><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AFBR<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AFBR \\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xem l\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd sinh h\\u1ecdc, d\\u1ef1a v\\u00e0o c\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a vi sinh v\\u1eadt ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 l\\u00e0m th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o 3 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y: qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh sinh h\\u1ecdc b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh; qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh t\\u00f9y nghi kh\\u1eed nito, photpho; qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh vi sinh v\\u1eadt sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 d\\u00ednh b\\u00e1m tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac. Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd c\\u00f3 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 hay kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e0o hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t x\\u1eed l\\u00fd v\\u00e0 tham gia tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u1edbi 3 ch\\u1ee7ng VSV d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ch\\u1ee7ng VSV ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng: achromobacter, alcaligenes, arthrobacter, citromonas, flavobacterium, zoogloea,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ch\\u1ee7ng VSV t\\u00f9y nghi: nitrosomonas, nitrobacter, nitrosopira, dethiobacillus, siderocapsa, methanonas, spirillum, denitrobacillus, moraxella, thiobaccillus, pseudomonas,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ch\\u1ee7ng VSV d\\u00ednh b\\u00e1m: arcanobacterium pyogenes, staphylococcus aureus,staphylococcus hyicus, streptococcus agalactiae, corynebacterium,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u01a1 s\\u1edf khoa h\\u1ecdc c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AFBR<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 nh\\u1edd vi sinh v\\u1eadt g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">sinh h\\u00f3a. \\u0110\\u1ec3 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh n\\u00e0y, c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 h\\u00f2a tan, c\\u1ea3 ch\\u1ea5t keo v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t ph\\u00e2n t\\u00e1n nh\\u1ecf trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i c\\u1ea7n di chuy\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0o b\\u00ean trong t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o vi sinh v\\u1eadt theo h\\u00ecnh nh\\u01b0 sau:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 Chuy\\u1ec3n c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m t\\u1eeb pha l\\u1ecfng t\\u1edbi b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o vi sinh v\\u1eadt;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 Khuy\\u1ebfch t\\u00e1n t\\u1eeb b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o qua m\\u00e0ng b\\u00e1n th\\u1ea5m do s\\u1ef1 ch\\u00eanh l\\u1ec7ch n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u00ean trong v\\u00e0 b\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 Chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t trong t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o vi sinh v\\u1eadt, s\\u1ea3n sinh n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 t\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o m\\u1edbi.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a sinh h\\u00f3a ph\\u1ee5 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1, h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 m\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee7a l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0o h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd. \\u1ede m\\u1ed7i \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh, c\\u00e1c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 ch\\u00ednh \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 ph\\u1ea3n \\u1ee9ng sinh h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 th\\u1ee7y \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng oxy trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i, nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9, pH, dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng v\\u00e0 nguy\\u00ean t\\u1ed1 vi l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd sinh h\\u1ecdc trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng AFBR g\\u1ed3m ba giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n sau:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1c vi sinh v\\u1eadt n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0 thu n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u00f3a th\\u00e0nh t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o m\\u1edbi, ch\\u1ec9 m\\u1ed9t ph\\u1ea7n ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 b\\u1ecb oxy h\\u00f3a ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh CO2, H2O, NO3-, SO42, \\u2026 M\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u1ed5ng qu\\u00e1t, vi sinh v\\u1eadt t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh bao g\\u1ed3m nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i vi khu\\u1ea9n kh\\u00e1c nhau c\\u00f9ng t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><em><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng AFBR v\\u1edbi sinh v\\u1eadt sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng d\\u1ea1ng l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng, qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y x\\u1ea3y ra khi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi b\\u00f9n trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1ee5c kh\\u00ed li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c. Vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1ee5c kh\\u00ed nh\\u1eb1m \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o c\\u00e1c y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u cung c\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u1ee7 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng oxy m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0 duy tr\\u00ec b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh \\u1edf tr\\u1ea1ng th\\u00e1i l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng. T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng oxy h\\u00f2a tan trong b\\u1ec3 b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh ph\\u1ee5 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 T\\u1ef7 s\\u1ed1 gi\\u1eefa l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n (CHC c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i) v\\u00e0 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng vi sinh v\\u1eadt: t\\u1ef7 l\\u1ec7 F\\/M;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 Nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng sinh l\\u00fd c\\u1ee7a vi sinh v\\u1eadt;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 N\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1ed9c t\\u00edch t\\u1ee5 trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ch\\u1ea5t;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 L\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea5u t\\u1ea1o t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2022 H\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng oxy h\\u00f2a tan.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh sinh h\\u1ecdc t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng d\\u00ednh b\\u00e1m<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 s\\u1ebd b\\u1ecb ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y b\\u1edfi qu\\u1ea7n th\\u1ec3 vi sinh v\\u1eadt d\\u00ednh b\\u00e1m tr\\u00ean l\\u1edbp v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc. C\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i s\\u1ebd b\\u1ecb h\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5 v\\u00e0o m\\u00e0ng vi sinh v\\u1eadt d\\u00e0y 0,1 \\u2013 0,2 mm v\\u00e0 b\\u1ecb ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y b\\u1edfi vi sinh v\\u1eadt hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed. Khi vi sinh v\\u1eadt sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n, b\\u1ec1 d\\u00e0y l\\u1edbp m\\u00e0ng t\\u0103ng l\\u00ean, do \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng oxy s\\u1ebd b\\u1ecb ti\\u00eau th\\u1ee5 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi khu\\u1ebfch t\\u00e1n h\\u1ebft chi\\u1ec1u d\\u00e0y l\\u1edbp m\\u00e0ng sinh v\\u1eadt. Nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady, m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng tu\\u1ef3 nghi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u00ecnh th\\u00e0nh ngay s\\u00e1t b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Khi chi\\u1ec1u d\\u00e0y l\\u1edbp m\\u00e0ng t\\u0103ng l\\u00ean, qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 x\\u1ea3y ra tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi ch\\u00fang ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi vi sinh v\\u1eadt g\\u1ea7n b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc. K\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 l\\u00e0 vi sinh v\\u1eadt \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e2y b\\u1ecb ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y n\\u1ed9i b\\u00e0o, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f2n kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng d\\u00ednh b\\u00e1m l\\u00ean b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 b\\u1ecb r\\u1eeda tr\\u00f4i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u1eed nit\\u01a1 (N)<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t nitrogen (N) v\\u00e0 phosphorus (P) trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0 nguy\\u00ean nh\\u00e2n g\\u00e2y ra hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ph\\u00fa d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng. Tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf P ra kh\\u1ecfi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p l\\u00fd ho\\u00e1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi chi ph\\u00ed x\\u1eed l\\u00fd cao.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh nitrat ho\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c di\\u1ec5n ra trong hai b\\u01b0\\u1edbc, b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1eb1ng amm\\u00f4ni\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chuy\\u1ec3n th\\u00e0nh nitr\\u00edt b\\u1edfi vi khu\\u1ea9n Nitrosomonas, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 nitr\\u00edt b\\u1ecb \\u00f4xy ho\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh nitr\\u00e1t do vi khu\\u1ea9n Nitrobacter. Hai lo\\u1ea1i vi khu\\u1ea9n n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng t\\u1ef1 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng AFBR v\\u00e0 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngu\\u1ed3n carbon dioxide l\\u00e0m ngu\\u1ed3n carbon trong t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang theo s\\u01a1 \\u0111\\u1ed3 ph\\u1ea3n \\u1ee9ng:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u1eed ph\\u1ed1tpho (P)<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ph\\u1ed1tpho l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t nguy\\u00ean t\\u1ed1 ch\\u00ednh r\\u1ea5t quan tr\\u1ecdng trong s\\u1ef1 s\\u1ed1ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed7i t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o, chi\\u1ebfm 1-3% t\\u1ed5ng tr\\u1ecdng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng kh\\u00f4 c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed7i t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o vi sinh v\\u1eadt. \\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi, ph\\u1ed1tpho l\\u00e0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 thi\\u1ebfu trong c\\u1ea5u t\\u1ea1o di truy\\u1ec1n AND, ARN.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">V\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ecdc, ph\\u1ed1tpho l\\u00e0 nguy\\u00ean nh\\u00e2n ch\\u00ednh g\\u00e2y ra hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ph\\u00fa d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ho\\u00e1, hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc do s\\u1ef1 gia t\\u0103ng kh\\u00f4ng ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t v\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 ch\\u1ebft h\\u00e0ng lo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i t\\u1ea3o v\\u00e0 thu\\u1ef7 sinh.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ph\\u1ed1tpho c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 ngu\\u1ed3n d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 quan tr\\u1ecdng trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0 sinh s\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c vi sinh v\\u1eadt trong h\\u1ec7 vi sinh c\\u1ed9ng sinh AFBR. Trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng AFBR d\\u01b0\\u1edbi t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 vi sinh c\\u1ed9ng sinh, Ph\\u1ed1tpho s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chuy\\u1ec3n ho\\u00e1 v\\u00e0 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Vi\\u1ec7c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf nit\\u01a1 &amp; ph\\u1ed1tpho theo ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p sinh h\\u1ecdc b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AFBR s\\u1ebd mang l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd cao \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft k\\u1ec7m chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh. C\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd d\\u00f9ng d\\u00f9ng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AFBR c\\u0169ng g\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eb9 v\\u00e0 d\\u1ec5 h\\u1ee3p kh\\u1ed1i, m\\u1edf ra tri\\u1ec3n v\\u1ecdng \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong d\\u00e2n d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1ea1i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam trong m\\u1ed9t t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai kh\\u00f4ng xa.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><em><strong>\\u01afu \\u0111i\\u1ec3m c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AFBR<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"color: #212529; font-family: roboto, arial; text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">H\\u1ec7 VSV c\\u1ed9ng sinh mang t\\u00ednh hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 cao<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u1ebfn 30% di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng sensor ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u1ebfn 40% \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u0103ng ti\\u00eau th\\u1ee5<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Chi ph\\u00ed l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t th\\u1ea5p<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Gi\\u1ea3m hao ph\\u00ed s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u0103ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m ngu\\u1ed3n h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">III.\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n, cao \\u1ed1c, resort v\\u00e0 chung c\\u01b0 nh\\u1eb1m ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">AFBR k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 h\\u00f3a l\\u00fd v\\u00e0 h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i trong m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 khu c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u00f3 quy m\\u00f4 l\\u1edbn.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">AFBR c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ABNR (Advance Biological Nutrient Removal) x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i ng\\u00e0nh th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m c\\u00f3 t\\u1ea3i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 cao.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","specification":"","media":""}', 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AFBR', 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AFBR', 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AFBR', 1, 64, 2, '2020-03-19 05:10:09', '2020-03-19 05:10:09');
