RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0\\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ea1t y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng sinh ho\\u1ea1t, an to\\u00e0n cho s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng theo quy chu\\u1ea9n QCVN:2009\\/BYT c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 Y T\\u1ebf ban h\\u00e0nh. H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1ea1i M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan\\u2026chi ph\\u00ed b\\u1ea3o d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng th\\u1ea5p, c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng thu h\\u1ed3i v\\u1ed1n nhanh, mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf c\\u1ea1nh tranh m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c doanh nghi\\u1ec7p trong c\\u00f9ng ng\\u00e0nh n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Ngam\\/He-thong-xu-ly-nguon-nuoc-ngam-thanh-nuoc-sinh-hoat-(4).png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"700\\" height=\\"700\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>II. GI\\u1ea2I PH\\u00c1P X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC NG\\u1ea6M<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 1. T\\u1ea1i sao ph\\u1ea3i s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u1ede Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, s\\u1ed1 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n, h\\u1ed9 gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m l\\u00e0 r\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn. V\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a n\\u1ec1n kinh t\\u1ebf \\u2013 c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 ch\\u1ee9a nhi\\u1ec1u kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng h\\u00f2a tan, ch\\u1ea5t r\\u1eafn l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng, vi sinh v\\u1eadt m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb x\\u00e2m nh\\u1eadp t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y, h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t n\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p trong tr\\u1ed3ng tr\\u1ecdt, r\\u00f2 r\\u1ec9 h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ed1 m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd, l\\u00e0m bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1nh t\\u1edbi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y ch\\u1ec9 ra r\\u1eb1ng c\\u1ea7n c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 cung c\\u1ea5p cho con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m an to\\u00e0n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Trong nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m k\\u1ec3 t\\u1eeb khi th\\u00e0nh l\\u1eadp, GMC VINA \\u0111\\u00e3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m cho nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u1ed9 d\\u00e2n c\\u01b0 v\\u00e0 nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t. K\\u1ec3 t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u00e3 l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u khu v\\u1ef1c b\\u1ecb \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m n\\u1eb7ng c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1, ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00f4 c\\u01a1 asen, crom, ch\\u00ec, perchlorate v\\u00e0 nitrat. Nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u l\\u00e0m n\\u00ean s\\u1ef1 kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 m\\u00e0 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cung c\\u1ea5p. \\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA \\u0111\\u00e3 gi\\u00fap x\\u1eed l\\u00fd h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n kh\\u00e1c nhau v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb ki\\u1ebfn \\u200b\\u200bth\\u1ee9c chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ec1 xu\\u1ea5t nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng chi ph\\u00ed th\\u1ea5p nh\\u1ea5t<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a02. C\\u00e1c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 C\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m. Trong m\\u1ed9t quy tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 kh\\u00e1c nhau t\\u00f9y theo t\\u1eebng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ri\\u00eang, v\\u00e0 nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\\u00ean c\\u00e1c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u00e2n lo\\u1ea1i ch\\u00fang th\\u00e0nh 2 nh\\u00f3m ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt l\\u00fd:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Trong x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m, m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ch\\u1ea5t h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u00eam\\u00a0ho\\u1eb7c tr\\u1ed9n v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t g\\u00e2y \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m khi ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ea1t hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 cao v\\u00e0 th\\u1eddi gian x\\u1eed l\\u00fd kh\\u00e1 nhanh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 \\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m ch\\u1ee9a nhi\\u1ec1u kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd b\\u1eb1ng ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion, ho\\u1eb7c v\\u00f4i, soda. Th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m c\\u00f3 h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1eaft cao c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf b\\u1eb1ng ch\\u1ea5t oxy h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ho\\u1eb7c l\\u00e0m tho\\u00e1ng b\\u1eb1ng gi\\u00e0n m\\u01b0a oxy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 \\u0110\\u1ec3 di\\u1ec7t khu\\u1ea9n ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t oxy h\\u00f3a h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc m\\u1ea1nh nh\\u01b0 kh\\u00ed ozone v\\u00e0 Clo l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng ch\\u1ea5t x\\u00fac t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 N\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ed9 pH th\\u1ea5p c\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ec1m h\\u00f3a b\\u1eb1ng h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t ammoniac (NH3).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u1ee9a nhi\\u1ec1u Oxy c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u00f9ng hydrazine, natrithisunfat,\\u2026 \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u1eed c\\u00e1c li\\u00ean k\\u1ebft.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd v\\u1eadt l\\u00fd<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd v\\u1eadt l\\u00fd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kh\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u trong x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m khi cho ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc qua c\\u00e1c b\\u1ed9 l\\u1ecdc c\\u00e1t, \\u0111\\u00e1, s\\u1ecfi,\\u2026 ho\\u1eb7c k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c m\\u00e0ng l\\u1ecdc RO, UF, NF hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i\\u00a0 c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd sinh h\\u1ecdc ho\\u1eb7c h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc cho ra ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea1t ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1eeb r\\u1ea5t l\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3m m\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn nay v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 X\\u1eed l\\u00fd b\\u1eb1ng nhi\\u1ec7t: l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p v\\u1eadt l\\u00fd th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u1edf quy m\\u00f4 nh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ec3 ti\\u00eau di\\u1ec7t vi khu\\u1ea9n. \\u0110a ph\\u1ea7n vi khu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb ti\\u00eau di\\u1ec7t \\u1edf 100 \\u0111\\u1ed9 C, b\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 nh\\u00f3m kh\\u00e1c b\\u1ecb ti\\u00eau di\\u1ec7t \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 cao h\\u01a1n kho\\u1ea3ng 200 \\u0111\\u1ed9 C.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 Trong c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, di\\u1ec7t khu\\u1ea9n b\\u1eb1ng tia UV th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u nh\\u1ea5t khi ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ecdc s\\u1ea1ch, kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ee9a c\\u00e1c c\\u1eb7n l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Nh\\u00ecn chung, c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 khi t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm m\\u1ed9t gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m. Gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m l\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 \\u2013 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p sinh h\\u1ecdc, h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc hay v\\u1eadt l\\u00fd, ph\\u1ee5 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ecba l\\u00fd, lo\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5t g\\u00e2y \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, chi ph\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u v\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t th\\u1eddi gian v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 kh\\u00e1c s\\u1ebd \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ebfn ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 3. M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng g\\u1eb7p trong x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1ch gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft<\\/strong>.<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><em style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a03.1. X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m nhi\\u1ec5m s\\u1eaft, mangan<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0C\\u00e1c kho\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y trong t\\u1ea7ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m nh\\u01b0 s\\u1eaft ho\\u1eb7c mangan c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf b\\u1eb1ng qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a, k\\u1ebft t\\u1ee7a v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 l\\u1ecdc.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0S\\u1eaft c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb oxy h\\u00f3a trong nhi\\u1ec1u tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch s\\u1ee5c kh\\u00ed. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb \\u1edf \\u0111\\u1ed9 pH t\\u1eeb 8 tr\\u1edf l\\u00ean s\\u1ebd th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a s\\u1eaft nhanh h\\u01a1n, trong tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 \\u1edf n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00e1ng k\\u1ec3. N\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 cao s\\u1ebd ng\\u0103n c\\u1ea3n hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd s\\u1eaft b\\u1eb1ng oxy h\\u00f3a h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc s\\u1eaft. C\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t nh\\u01b0 Clo, kali permanganat, Clo dioxide ho\\u1eb7c ozone c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 oxy h\\u00f3a s\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 mangan. Kali permanganat th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho mangan.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: center;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Ngam\\/He-thong-xu-ly-nguon-nuoc-ngam-thanh-nuoc-sinh-hoat-5.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"683\\" height=\\"385\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<em style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">3.2. C\\u00e1ch x\\u1eed l\\u00fd amoni trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0GMC VINA xin gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd amoni trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u1ea1t trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion: khi qua b\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc cationit, c\\u00e1c h\\u1ea1t cation s\\u1ebd gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i ion Nh4+, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi ion Na+ trong ion \\u0111i ra ngo\\u00e0i m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00e0ng RO: lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf 99% c\\u00e1c ion, kho\\u00e1ng, c\\u1eb7n b\\u1ea9n, vi khu\\u1ea9n, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi c\\u0169ng gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c ion Nh4+.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u2013 Oxy h\\u00f3a b\\u1eb1ng Oxy, d\\u01b0\\u1edbi t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a vi khu\\u1ea9n Nitrosomonas oxi h\\u00f3a NH4+ th\\u00e0nh NO2- v\\u00e0 vi khu\\u1ea9n Nitrobacter oxy h\\u00f3a NO2-th\\u00e0nh NO3-\\u00a0theo ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">NH4+ + 2O2 \\u2192 NO3- + 2H+ + H2O<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">1.02NH4++ 1.89O2 + 2.02HCO3- \\u2192 0.21C5H7O2N + 1.0NO3- + 1.92 H2CO3 + 1.06H2O<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>II. H\\u00ccNH \\u1ea2NH &amp; VIDEO.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Ngam\\/He-thong-xu-ly-nguon-nuoc-ngam-thanh-nuoc-sinh-hoat-(4).png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"605\\" height=\\"605\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Ngam\\/He-thong-xu-ly-nguon-nuoc-ngam-thanh-nuoc-sinh-hoat-6.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"602\\" height=\\"452\\" \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><em style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Ngam\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Cap-Sinh-Hoat-Bang-Sieu-Mang-Loc-UF-VSIP---1.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"602\\" height=\\"440\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><em style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea5p sinh ho\\u1ea1t b\\u1eb1ng m\\u00e0ng l\\u1ecdc UF<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>IV. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG N\\u1ed4I B\\u1eacT.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1eeb\\u00a0M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u2013 H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u2013 C\\u00f3 thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ng\\u1eaft m\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u00e1y ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh khi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n \\u00e1p l\\u00ean xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u2013 V\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ecbu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft kh\\u1eafc nghi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n cho thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nh\\u1ecf g\\u1ecdn, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, t\\u1ed1n \\u00edt di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>V. \\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng d\\u00f9ng trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m \\u1edf nh\\u1eefng\\u00a0<span style=\\"font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">n\\u01a1i ch\\u01b0a c\\u00f3 h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u00e1y nh\\u01b0 v\\u00f9ng n\\u00fai xa x\\u00f4i, v\\u00f9ng n\\u00f4ng th\\u00f4n, n\\u01a1i ch\\u1ee9a nhi\\u1ec1u kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng h\\u00f2a tan, ch\\u1ea5t r\\u1eafn l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng, vi sinh v\\u1eadt m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb x\\u00e2m nh\\u1eadp t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y, h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t n\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p trong tr\\u1ed3ng tr\\u1ecdt, r\\u00f2 r\\u1ec9 h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ed1 m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd, l\\u00e0m bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1nh t\\u1edbi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>VI. QUY TR\\u00ccNH D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 L\\u1eaeP \\u0110\\u1eb6T H\\u1ec6 TH\\u1ed0NG\\u00a0X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC NG\\u1ea6M T\\u1ea0I GMC VINA.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1: Ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA\\u00a0Ho\\u1eb7c g\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i qua Hotline:\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 2: Kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf (Ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u00e0, c\\u00f4ng ty, c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra, kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 3: T\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p b\\u00e1o gi\\u00e1 d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt t\\u01b0.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 4: K\\u00fd h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh thi c\\u00f4ng (Nhanh ch\\u00f3ng k\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3 ngo\\u00e0i gi\\u1edd h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh, th\\u1ee9 7 v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eadt)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 5: B\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>VII. L\\u00dd DO B\\u1ea0N N\\u00caN CH\\u1eccN GMC VINA KH\\u00d4NG PH\\u1ea2I L\\u00c0 \\u0110\\u01a0N V\\u1eca N\\u00c0O KH\\u00c1C<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb chuy\\u00ean v\\u1ec1 x\\u01b0 l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0quy m\\u00f4 l\\u1edbn, nh\\u1ecf\\u00a0v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 s\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">Am hi\\u1ec3u s\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7c th\\u00f9 y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd t\\u1eebng l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">Chuy\\u00ean x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1eefng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00f3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p, \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec1u khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ecba h\\u00ecnh kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao t\\u1eeb M\\u1ef9, EU.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">B\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh h\\u1eadu m\\u00e3i nhanh ch\\u00f3ng b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec tr\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1eddi.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">GMC VINA\\u00a0\\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u trong vi\\u1ec7c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf, x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m cho nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u1ed9 d\\u00e2n c\\u01b0 v\\u00e0 nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, khu v\\u1ef1c b\\u1ecb \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m n\\u1eb7ng c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1, ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00f4 c\\u01a1 asen, crom, ch\\u00ec, perchlorate v\\u00e0 nitrat. Nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u l\\u00e0m n\\u00ean s\\u1ef1 kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 m\\u00e0 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cung c\\u1ea5p. \\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA \\u0111\\u00e3 gi\\u00fap x\\u1eed l\\u00fd h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n kh\\u00e1c nhau v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb ki\\u1ebfn \\u200b\\u200bth\\u1ee9c chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ec1 xu\\u1ea5t nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng chi ph\\u00ed th\\u1ea5p nh\\u1ea5t<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp; C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh:\\u00a0<\\/strong>S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>VPGD:\\u00a0<\\/strong>T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>\\u0110i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i:\\u00a0<\\/strong>02466 835383 - \\u00a0Fax: 02466.835383<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>Hotline:<\\/strong>\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>Website:\\u00a0<\\/strong><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/gmcwater.com\\/\\">https:\\/\\/gmcwater.com\\/<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","specification":"","media":""}', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Ngáº§m', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Ngáº§m', 'Há»‡ Thá»‘ng Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Ngáº§m', 0, 63, 2, '2020-03-19 09:58:54', '2020-03-19 09:58:54'),
(134, 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AAO ( A2O)', NULL, NULL, '', '{"detail":"<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u00f3ng m\\u1ed9t vai tr\\u00f2 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t quan tr\\u1ecdng v\\u00e0 \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1edbi hi\\u1ec7u xu\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i. \\u0110\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u hi\\u1ec3n nhi\\u00ean, kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i, m\\u00e0 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c n\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 c\\u0169ng lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 then ch\\u1ed1t, t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ee9c b\\u1eadt cho h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng. Y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u00e0 ngo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea3nh, v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed7i \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n kh\\u00e1c nhau l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng nh\\u1eefng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 v\\u00e0 gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p kh\\u00e1c nhau. L\\u1ea1i n\\u00f3i v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u00ea x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i, h\\u00f4m nay GMC VINA m\\u1eddi c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f9ng \\u0111i t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u00ea x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i\\u00a0C\\u00f4ng AAO ( A2O).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">I.\\u00a0 GI\\u1edaI THI\\u1ec6U C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC TH\\u1ea2I\\u00a0AAO ( A2O)<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">AAO hay c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 A2O bao g\\u1ed3m 3 giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n x\\u1eed l\\u00fd sau \\u0111\\u00e2y: Anaerobic (k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed) \\u2013 Anoxic (thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed) \\u2013 Oxic (hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed). C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i A2O l\\u00e0 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p sinh h\\u1ecdc nh\\u1edd v\\u00e0o s\\u1ef1 sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 vi sinh v\\u1eadt nh\\u01b0: VSV k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed, VSV thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed v\\u00e0 VSV k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed. Nh\\u1edd qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd khi h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 (ch\\u1ea5t \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i) m\\u00e0 ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1ea1t chu\\u1ea9n theo quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 T\\u00e0i nguy\\u00ean v\\u00e0 M\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">II. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC TH\\u1ea2I\\u00a0AAO ( A2O)<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Nguy\\u00ean l\\u00fd v\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AAO<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 AAO tr\\u1ea3i qua 3 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><em><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh sinh h\\u1ecdc k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed (Anearobic)<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">B\\u1ec3 sinh h\\u1ecdc k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i c\\u00e1c vi sinh k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd v\\u00e0 tham gia qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 h\\u00f2a tan. V\\u1eady l\\u00e0m th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ec3 vi sinh v\\u1eadt sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ch\\u00fang s\\u1ebd h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t kho\\u00e1ng c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u00f3a th\\u00e0nh th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n v\\u00e0 sinh ra c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u1edf d\\u1ea1ng kh\\u00ed.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u1ede \\u0111\\u00e2y m\\u00e1y s\\u1ee5c kh\\u00ed ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng cho to\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 h\\u1ec7 vi sinh v\\u1eadt. C\\u00e1c b\\u1ecdt kh\\u00ed \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c sinh ra, c\\u00e1c h\\u1ea1t b\\u00f9n c\\u1eb7n b\\u00e1m v\\u00e0o b\\u1ecdt kh\\u00ed v\\u00e0 tho\\u00e1t ra ngo\\u00e0i nh\\u1edd thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u1edbt b\\u1ecdt.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u00e1c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc tham gia v\\u00e0o qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 c\\u1ee7a vi sinh v\\u1eadt trong c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i AAO:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 + VK k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed \\u2192 CO2 + H2S + CH4 + c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t kh\\u00e1c + n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 + VK k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed + n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u2192 C5H7O2N (T\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o vi khu\\u1ea9n m\\u1edbi)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed di\\u1ec5n ra trong 4 giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 1: Th\\u1ee7y ph\\u00e2n<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2: Acid h\\u00f3a<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 3: Acetane h\\u00f3a<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 4: Methane h\\u00f3a<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh sinh h\\u1ecdc thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed (Anoxic)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">H\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i ch\\u1ee9a h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nito v\\u00e0 photpho kh\\u00e1 cao, v\\u00ec th\\u1ebf 2 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0y ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd tri\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3. T\\u1ea1i b\\u1ec3 Anoxic di\\u1ec5n ra qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u1eed N v\\u00e0 P nh\\u1edd c\\u00e1c vi sinh v\\u1eadt hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cung c\\u1ea5p oxy. Song song, 2 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh Nitrat h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 Photphoril x\\u1ea3y ra \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi kh\\u1eed ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9c h\\u1ea1i trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh nitrat h\\u00f3a<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">L\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 t\\u1eeb hai ch\\u1ee7ng lo\\u1ea1i vi khu\\u1ea9n Nitrosonas v\\u00e0 Nitrobacter. Trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thi\\u1ebfu oxy, nitrat h\\u00f3a x\\u1ea3y ra trong 2 giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n sau:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed3ng h\\u00f3a: di\\u1ec5n ra qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u1eed NO3 =&gt; Nh4+<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">D\\u1ecb h\\u00f3a: kh\\u1eed NO3 =&gt; NO2 =&gt; N2O =&gt; N2<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Kh\\u00ed nito \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1edd bay h\\u01a1i v\\u00e0 tho\\u00e1t ra kh\\u1ecfi ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh photphorit h\\u00f3a<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Nh\\u1edd s\\u1ef1 tham gia c\\u1ee7a vi khu\\u1ea9n Acinetobacter m\\u00e0 h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng photpho \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t m\\u1edbi m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 tham gia c\\u1ee7a photpho ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t m\\u1edbi ch\\u1ee9a th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n photpho nh\\u01b0ng l\\u1ea1i d\\u1ec5 ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y b\\u1edfi vi khu\\u1ea9n Acinetobacter.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng, b\\u1ec3 Anoxic \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed th\\u00eam m\\u00e1y khu\\u1ea5y ch\\u00ecm gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m x\\u00e1o tr\\u1ed9n ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng thi\\u1ebfu oxy gi\\u00fap h\\u1ec7 vi sinh v\\u1eadt thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n. Nh\\u1edd v\\u1eady m\\u00e0 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh nitrat h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 photpho di\\u1ec5n ra thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i h\\u01a1n.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><em><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i AAO<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh sinh h\\u1ecdc hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed (Oxic)<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">To\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i t\\u1ea1i b\\u1ec3 sinh h\\u1ecdc hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed nh\\u1edd v\\u00e0o ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ee7a vi sinh hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n oxy, n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 pH,\\u2026 th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, VSV s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng nito v\\u00e0 photpho trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o m\\u1edbi, CO2, H2O v\\u00e0 gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00f3ng n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ngo\\u00e0i ra, c\\u00e1c sinh v\\u1eadt t\\u1ef1 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng tham gia v\\u00e0o qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh nitrat h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 sunfat h\\u00f3a khi ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y kh\\u00ed NH4+ v\\u00e0 H2S.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 3 giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n x\\u1eed l\\u00fd sinh h\\u1ecdc hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 1: Oxy h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 th\\u1ee7y ph\\u00e2n c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1: Ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 + O2 \\u00e0 CO2 + H2O + n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2: T\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o m\\u1edbi: Ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 + O2 + NH3 \\u00e0 T\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o VSV + CO2 + H2O + n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 3: Ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y n\\u1ed9i sinh: C5H7O2N + O2 \\u00e0 CO2 + H2O + NH3 + n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><strong><em><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u01afu \\u0111i\\u1ec3m c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i AAO (A2O)<\\/span><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng BOD trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i kh\\u00e1 cao t\\u1eeb 90 \\u2013 95%<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m chi ph\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m th\\u1eddi gian ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 di d\\u1eddi h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh th\\u1ea5p<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">X\\u1eed l\\u00fd hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u00f4 nhi\\u1ec5m trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">C\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">D\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng l\\u1eafp th\\u00eam c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb m\\u1edbi m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n th\\u00e1o d\\u1ee1 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 m\\u1ea5u n\\u1ed1i hay thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb n\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","specification":"","media":""}', 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AAO ( A2O)', 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AAO ( A2O)', 'CÃ´ng Nghá»‡ Xá»­ LÃ½ NÆ°á»›c Tháº£i AAO ( A2O)', 1, 64, 2, '2020-03-19 10:27:16', '2020-03-19 10:27:16');
