1ecfe ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng theo quy chu\\u1ea9n QCVN:2009\\/BYT c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 Y T\\u1ebf ban h\\u00e0nh. H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1ea1i M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan\\u2026chi ph\\u00ed b\\u1ea3o d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng th\\u1ea5p, c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng thu h\\u1ed3i v\\u1ed1n nhanh, mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf c\\u1ea1nh tranh m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c doanh nghi\\u1ec7p trong c\\u00f9ng ng\\u00e0nh n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img style=\\"undefined\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Gieng%20Khoan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Gieng-Khoan-Cong-Nghep-4.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"700\\" height=\\"525\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>II. GI\\u1ea2I PH\\u00c1P X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC GI\\u1ebeNG KHOAN C\\u00d4NG NGHI\\u1ec6P<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-size: 16.38px; font-family: inherit;\\">1. T\\u1ea1i sao c\\u1ea7n khoan gi\\u1ebfng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ol style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-size: 14px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc cung c\\u1ea5p cho nhu c\\u1ea7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ee7, qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch ph\\u1ea3i ch\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ee3i<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 chi tr\\u1ea3 cho n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea1ch \\u0111ang v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qu\\u00e1 d\\u1ef1 to\\u00e1n chi ph\\u00ed kinh doanh c\\u1ee7a qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u1ea7n ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m ti\\u1ec1n ngay t\\u1eeb ti\\u1ec1n ph\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ea3 h\\u00e0ng th\\u00e1ng cho n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea1ch<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">V\\u1eady qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f2n ch\\u1edd g\\u00ec m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngay\\u00a0<strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan<\\/strong>, m\\u1ed9t ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 s\\u1eb5n trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft h\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c lo ng\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">GMC VINA \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1up n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c\\u00a0<strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">khoan gi\\u1ebfng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p<\\/strong>, khoan gi\\u1ebfng d\\u00e2n d\\u1ee5ng, xin \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u t\\u1edbi qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1\\u00a0<strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">gi\\u1ebfng khoan c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p<\\/strong>\\u00a0v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c k\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ecf kh\\u00e1c nhau m\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ty \\u0111\\u00e3 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n sau \\u0111\\u00e2y v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t gi\\u00e1 r\\u1ebb nh\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ol style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-size: 14px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i \\u03a690 : l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trung b\\u00ecnh trong kho\\u1ea3ng 2 \\u2013 6m3\\/h (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m &amp; khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i \\u03a6110 : l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trung b\\u00ecnh trong kho\\u1ea3ng 4 \\u2013 15m3\\/h (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m &amp; khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i \\u03a6125 : l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trung b\\u00ecnh trong kho\\u1ea3ng 8 \\u2013 30m3\\/h (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m &amp; khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i \\u03a6160 : l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trung b\\u00ecnh trong kho\\u1ea3ng 10 \\u2013 60m3\\/h (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m &amp; khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i \\u03a6219 : l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trung b\\u00ecnh trong kho\\u1ea3ng 15 \\u2013 100m3\\/h (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m &amp; khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1eddng k\\u00ednh \\u1ed1ng ngo\\u00e0i \\u03a6325 : l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trung b\\u00ecnh trong kho\\u1ea3ng 20 \\u2013 150m3\\/h (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m &amp; khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">T\\u00f9y theo theo t\\u1eebng nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n n\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng lo\\u1ea1i n\\u00e0o cho ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t. Lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ebfng c\\u00f3 c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb 3 m3\\/h tr\\u1edf l\\u00ean ph\\u1ee5c v\\u1ee5 cho: nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd, c\\u01a1 quan, khu t\\u1eadp th\\u1ec3, nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y, c\\u00f4ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng thi c\\u00f4ng\\u2026 Lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ebfng n\\u00e0y c\\u1ea7n thi c\\u00f4ng b\\u1eb1ng gi\\u00e0n m\\u00e1y khoan, thi c\\u00f4ng khoan s\\u00e2u t\\u1eeb 30 \\u2013 280m (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o t\\u1eebng khu v\\u1ef1c), th\\u1eddi gian thi c\\u00f4ng t\\u1eeb 2 \\u2013 45 ng\\u00e0y (t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o t\\u1eebng lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ebfng), l\\u1ea5y n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u1ecba t\\u1ea7ng 2 ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u1ecba t\\u1ea7ng 3 n\\u00ean n\\u01b0\\u1edbc l\\u00ean s\\u1ea1ch h\\u01a1n ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n. gi\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh t\\u1eeb 9 \\u2013 200 tri\\u1ec7u\\/ gi\\u1ebfng ( t\\u00f9y v\\u00e0o t\\u1eebng lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ebfng v\\u00e0 khu v\\u1ef1c khoan)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif; text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Gieng%20Khoan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Gieng-Khoan-Cong-Nghep-3.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"731\\" height=\\"548\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi khoan c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb nh\\u1eefng g\\u00ec?<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-size: 14px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">M\\u1eb7t b\\u1eb1ng r\\u1ed9ng: 2 m, da\\u0300i 3 m, cao 4m (tr\\u1edf l\\u00ean)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">N\\u01b0\\u1edbc: tr\\u00ean 3 m3 ( Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ec3 khoan c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0: n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea1ch \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 s\\u1eb5n, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00f3, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f4ng, h\\u1ed3, ao, m\\u01b0\\u01a1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u1edf g\\u1ea7n \\u0111i\\u1ec3m khoan\\u2026)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">S\\u1ecfi ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u00e1 Ganito: 3 \\u2013 5 bao<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ee7 kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m\\u00e1y khoan c\\u00f3 c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t 5-6 kw\\/h<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">M\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m d\\u00f9ng cho lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ebfng n\\u00e0y l\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y b\\u01a1m ch\\u00ecm (b\\u01a1m h\\u1ecfa ti\\u1ec5n ho\\u1eb7c b\\u01a1m t\\u00f5m) CS 500W \\u2013 25 KW<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh: lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ebfng n\\u00e0y ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh 2 n\\u0103m v\\u1ec1 ngu\\u1ed3n c\\u1ea5p n\\u01b0\\u1edbc<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\\">Quy tr\\u00ecnh khoan gi\\u1ebfng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p theo c\\u00e1c b\\u01b0\\u1edbc sau:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-size: 14px; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed khoan gi\\u1ebfng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ed9 s\\u00e2u c\\u1ee7a gi\\u1ebfng, ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan, lo\\u1ea1i \\u1ed1ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng l\\u1eafp gi\\u1ebfng, lo\\u1ea1i b\\u01a1m s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Th\\u1ed1ng nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng s\\u1ed1 v\\u1ec1 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, th\\u1eddi gian, chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1edbi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">K\\u00fd h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng v\\u1edbi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Khoan gi\\u1ebfng: qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh khoan gi\\u1ebfng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt cao \\u0111\\u1ea3m nhi\\u1ec7m t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng m\\u0169i khoan \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi c\\u00f3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u00e0o s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">B\\u00e0n giao, nghi\\u1ec7m thu thanh l\\u00fd h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng:\\u00a0 Gi\\u1ebfng ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c To\\u00e0n \\u00c1 b\\u00e0n giao khi \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng ty v\\u00e0 y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">B\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c: kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh gi\\u1ebfng trong v\\u00f2ng 1 n\\u0103m, ngo\\u00e0i ra GMC VINA c\\u00f2n \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3i \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u00e3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA (Nh\\u01b0 gi\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1, b\\u1ea3o d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed \\u2026)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3 style=\\"color: #3d3d3d; font-family: RobotoCondensed-Light, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>3. H\\u00ccNH \\u1ea2NH &amp; VIDEO.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Gieng%20Khoan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Gieng-Khoan-Cong-Nghep-0.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"700\\" height=\\"700\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Gieng%20Khoan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Gieng-Khoan-Cong-Nghep-1.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"701\\" height=\\"934\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Gieng%20Khoan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Gieng-Khoan-Cong-Nghep-2.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"700\\" height=\\"461\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/He%20Thong%20Xu%20Ly%20Nuoc%20Cap\\/Nuoc%20Gieng%20Khoan\\/He-Thong-Xu-Ly-Nuoc-Gieng-Khoan-Cong-Nghep-4.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"702\\" height=\\"526\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>4. T\\u00cdNH N\\u0102NG N\\u1ed4I B\\u1eacT.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u t\\u1eeb\\u00a0M\\u1ef9, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, H\\u00e0 Lan.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2013 H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2013 C\\u00f3 thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ng\\u1eaft m\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u00e1y ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh khi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n \\u00e1p l\\u00ean xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2013 V\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ecbu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1eddi ti\\u1ebft kh\\u1eafc nghi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n cho thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u2013 Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf nh\\u1ecf g\\u1ecdn, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, t\\u1ed1n \\u00edt di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>5. \\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng d\\u00f9ng trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc\\u00a0c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan, s\\u1eaft tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sinh ho\\u1ea1t chung.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>6. QUY TR\\u00ccNH D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 L\\u1eaeP \\u0110\\u1eb6T H\\u1ec6 TH\\u1ed0NG\\u00a0X\\u1eec L\\u00dd N\\u01af\\u1edaC GI\\u1ebeNG KHOAN C\\u00d4NG NGHI\\u1ec6P T\\u1ea0I GMC VINA.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1: Ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA\\u00a0Ho\\u1eb7c g\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i qua Hotline:\\u00a0<strong>098 998 0178<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 2: Kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf (Ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt c\\u1ee7a GMC VINA s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u00e0, c\\u00f4ng ty, c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra, kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 3: T\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p b\\u00e1o gi\\u00e1 d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt t\\u01b0.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 4: K\\u00fd h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh thi c\\u00f4ng (Nhanh ch\\u00f3ng k\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3 ngo\\u00e0i gi\\u1edd h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh, th\\u1ee9 7 v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eadt)<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong><em>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 5: B\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>7. L\\u00dd DO B\\u1ea0N N\\u00caN CH\\u1eccN GMC VINA KH\\u00d4NG PH\\u1ea2I L\\u00c0 \\u0110\\u01a0N V\\u1eca N\\u00c0O KH\\u00c1C<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">\\u0110\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb chuy\\u00ean v\\u1ec1 x\\u01b0 l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0quy m\\u00f4 l\\u1edbn, nh\\u1ecf\\u00a0v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 k\\u1ef9 s\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Am hi\\u1ec3u s\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7c th\\u00f9 y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd t\\u1eebng l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Chuy\\u00ean x\\u1eed l\\u00fd nh\\u1eefng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u00f3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p, \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec1u khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ecba h\\u00ecnh kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao t\\u1eeb M\\u1ef9, EU.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">B\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh h\\u1eadu m\\u00e3i nhanh ch\\u00f3ng b\\u1ea3o tr\\u00ec tr\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1eddi.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\">Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay v\\u1edbi\\u00a0C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA\\u00a0h\\u00f4m nay \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m tra n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.\\u00a0\\u00a0GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean cung c\\u1ea5p h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan d\\u00e2n d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p. \\u0110\\u1ec3 bi\\u1ebft ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 bao nhi\\u00eau, h\\u00e3y li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ty ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p, ph\\u1ee5 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o nhi\\u1ec1u y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 kh\\u00e1c nhau nh\\u01b0: n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 Mangan trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, s\\u1eaft, \\u0111\\u1ed9 ki\\u1ec1m, sunfua, amoniac v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 carbon h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 h\\u00f2a tan, c\\u00f4ng su\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p, kinh t\\u1ebf nh\\u1ea5t. Nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn, \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 v\\u00e0o h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng v\\u1edbi v\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u, chi ph\\u00ed v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh, h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t, x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ch\\u1ea5t th\\u1ea3i\\u2026 th\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp; C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh:\\u00a0<\\/strong>S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\"><strong>VPGD:\\u00a0<\\/strong>T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helv