(194, 'Than hoáº¡t tÃ­nh Calgon ÃšC', NULL, NULL, '<ul>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">HÃ¬nh dáº¡ng: dáº¡ng háº¡t, mÃ u Ä‘en, nhiá»u gÃ³c cáº¡nh</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">KÃ­ch cá»¡ háº¡t: 8-16 mesh</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Chá»‰ sá»‘ iodine: tá»‘i thiá»ƒu 900</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Quy cÃ¡ch: 20 kg/bao (tÆ°Æ¡ng Ä‘Æ°Æ¡ng khoáº£ng 50L)</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Calgon lÃ  thÆ°Æ¡ng hiá»‡u lá»›n xuáº¥t xá»© tá»« Má»¹, Ä‘Æ°á»£c sáº£n xuáº¥t táº¡i Ãšc</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Ráº¥t nhiá»u loáº¡i táº¡p cháº¥t Ä‘á»™c háº¡i Ä‘Æ°á»£c than háº¥p thá»¥</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;">Than hoáº¡t tÃ­nh Calgon ráº¥t thÃ´ng dá»¥ng trong cÃ´ng nghá»‡ xá»­ lÃ½ nÆ°á»›c tinh khiáº¿t vÃ  siÃªu tinh khiáº¿t, xá»­ lÃ½ nÆ°á»›c sinh hoáº¡t</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '{"detail":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh Calgon \\u00daC \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng, uy t\\u00edn ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 CO\\/CQ xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9.\\u00a0Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Than%20Calgon%20UC\\/Than-hoat-tinh-Calgon.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">1. \\u0110\\u1eb6C \\u0110I\\u1ec2M &amp; TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT.<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><strong>THAN HO\\u1ea0T T\\u00cdNH L\\u00c0 G\\u00cc?<\\/strong><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ch\\u1ea5t g\\u1ed3m ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu l\\u00e0 nguy\\u00ean t\\u1ed1 carbon \\u1edf d\\u1ea1ng v\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh h\\u00ecnh (b\\u1ed9t), m\\u1ed9t ph\\u1ea7n n\\u1eefa c\\u00f3 d\\u1ea1ng tinh th\\u1ec3 v\\u1ee5n grafit (ngo\\u00e0i carbon th\\u00ec ph\\u1ea7n c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i th\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00e0 t\\u00e0n tro, m\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c kim lo\\u1ea1i ki\\u1ec1m v\\u00e0 v\\u1ee5n c\\u00e1t).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">B\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ri\\u00eang r\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn c\\u1ee7a than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a c\\u1ea5u tr\\u00fac x\\u01a1 r\\u1ed7ng m\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu l\\u00e0 do th\\u1eeba h\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1eeb nguy\\u00ean li\\u1ec7u h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9, qua qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u01b0ng kh\\u00f4 (s\\u1ea5y) \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 cao, trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed. Ph\\u1ea7n l\\u1edbn c\\u00e1c v\\u1ebft r\\u1ed7ng \\u2013 n\\u1ee9t vi m\\u1ea1ch, \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u00f3 t\\u00ednh h\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5 r\\u1ea5t m\\u1ea1nh v\\u00e0 ch\\u00fang \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 c\\u00e1c r\\u00e3nh chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1ea3i (k\\u1ebd n\\u1ed1i).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh c\\u00f3 di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ngo\\u00e0i r\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn, do v\\u1eady m\\u00e0 n\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ch\\u1ea5t l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng d\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc h\\u00fat nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Than th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ef1 n\\u00e2ng c\\u1ea5p (v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5, t\\u1ef1 r\\u1eeda tro ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t tr\\u00e1ng m\\u1eb7t), \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u01b0u gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eefng thu\\u1ed9c t\\u00ednh l\\u1ecdc h\\u00fat, \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 th\\u1ea5m h\\u00fat \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u01b0 kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><strong>THAN HO\\u1ea0T T\\u00cdNH CALGON<\\/strong><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Calgon l\\u00e0 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u l\\u1edbn xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9 t\\u1eeb M\\u1ef9 v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed l\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u1eddi th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi. \\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m t\\u1eeb than b\\u00f9n ho\\u1ea1t h\\u00f3a b\\u1eb1ng h\\u01a1i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 cao trong \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">R\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9c h\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c than h\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5: Chlorine; C\\u1eb7n th\\u00f4; H\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1; M\\u00f9i h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t; Ph\\u00e2n b\\u00f3n, thu\\u1ed1c tr\\u1eeb s\\u00e2u; TCE (Trichloroethylene); B\\u1ed9t gi\\u1eb7t; EDB (Ethylene dibromide); Chloramines; THM (Trihalomethanes); V\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t kh\\u00e1c, \\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh Calgonr\\u1ea5t th\\u00f4ng d\\u1ee5ng trong\\u00a0c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc tinh khi\\u1ebft\\u00a0v\\u00e0 si\\u00eau tinh khi\\u1ebft,\\u00a0x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sinh ho\\u1ea1t\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong><strong>TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT C\\u1ee6A THAN HO\\u1ea0T T\\u00cdNH CALGON HPC SUPER 830<\\/strong><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">H\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea1ng: d\\u1ea1ng h\\u1ea1t, m\\u00e0u \\u0111en, nhi\\u1ec1u g\\u00f3c c\\u1ea1nh<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">K\\u00edch c\\u1ee1 h\\u1ea1t: 8-16 mesh<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1ed1 iodine: t\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ec3u 900<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m: &lt; 10%<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">H\\u1ec7 s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng nh\\u1ea5t: 1.8<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">T\\u1ec9 tr\\u1ecdng: 400kg\\/m3<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Quy c\\u00e1ch: 20 kg\\/bao (t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng kho\\u1ea3ng 50L)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VAI TR\\u00d2 C\\u1ee6A THAN HO\\u1ea0T T\\u00cdNH CALGON<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf m\\u00f9i, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Kh\\u1eed m\\u00e0u;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">H\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5 nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9c h\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0: Chlorine; C\\u1eb7n th\\u00f4; H\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1; M\\u00f9i h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t; Ph\\u00e2n b\\u00f3n, thu\\u1ed1c tr\\u1eeb s\\u00e2u; TCE (Trichloroethylene); B\\u1ed9t gi\\u1eb7t; EDB (Ethylene dibromide); Chloramines; THM (Trihalomethanes); V\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t kh\\u00e1c, \\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1ed1t cho x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng, y t\\u1ebf, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t d\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ea9m, linh ki\\u1ec7n \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Than%20Calgon%20UC\\/Than-hoat-tinh-Calgon-1.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"627\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. CH\\u00cdNH S\\u00c1CH B\\u00c1N H\\u00c0NG C\\u1ee6A GMCVINA<\\/strong><br \\/><br \\/><strong>GMCWATER.COM\\u00a0<\\/strong>t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u va\\u0300 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00e2m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u201cLan t\\u1ecfa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng\\u201d th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch sau::<br \\/><br \\/><strong>GI\\u00c1 T\\u1eacN G\\u1ed0C:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA l\\u00e0 nha\\u0300 nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u, ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng t\\u01b0\\u0300 ca\\u0301c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u00ea\\u0323u l\\u01a1\\u0301n \\u0111\\u00ea\\u0301n t\\u01b0\\u0300 Nh\\u1eadt, H\\u00e0n, EU, M\\u1ef9 n\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M M\\u01a0\\u0301I 100%:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA ch\\u1ec9 b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng m\\u1edbi 100% c\\u00f2n nguy\\u00ean \\u0111ai nguy\\u00ean ki\\u1ec7n<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M CH\\u00cdNH H\\u00c3NG:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA s\\u1ebd g\\u1eedi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng xem tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn CO (Xu\\u1ea5t X\\u1ee9) + CQ (Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng), s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u00e1i\\/ c\\u0169 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 2 lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1n 10 l\\u1ea7n gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb mua h\\u00e0ng n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng nh\\u00e1i\\/ h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169 k\\u00e9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG L\\u00c0 S\\u1ed0 1:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb7t nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng l\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng mua thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1i\\u00a0gmcwater.com\\u00a0ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee9c chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd<br \\/><br \\/><strong>D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 T\\u1ed0T NH\\u1ea4T:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n 24\\/24 trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh mua v\\u00e0 sau mua. B\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 khi n\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng g\\u1eb7p v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong th\\u1eddi gian nhanh nh\\u1ea5t.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH D\\u00c0I H\\u1ea0N:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ngo\\u00e0i ph\\u1ea7n b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u00e3ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh ri\\u00eang t\\u1eeb ph\\u00eda GMC VINA theo ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">LI\\u00caN H\\u1ec6:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">MST: 0107998239 do S\\u1edf K\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i c\\u1ea5p ng\\u00e0y 20\\/09\\/2017<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh: S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VPGD: T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VPGD chi nh\\u00e1nh TP. HCM\\u00a0: s\\u1ed1\\u00a092\\/20B\\/20\\/17 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Ph\\u1ea1m H\\u00f9ng, Ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng 4, Qu\\u1eadn 8, TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-famil