(196, 'Háº¡t Cation S1567 Lanxess ', NULL, NULL, '<ul>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Dáº¡ng Gel, Acid máº¡nh, cÃ³ phÃ¢n bá»‘ kÃ­ch thÆ°á»›c háº¡t tiÃªu chuáº©n</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">ÄÆ°á»£c sáº£n xuáº¥t theo cÃ´ng nghá»‡ khÃ´ng sá»­ dá»¥ng dung mÃ´i hÃ³a cháº¥t nÃªn Ä‘áº¡t chá»©ng chá»‰ FDA dÃ¹ng trong ngÃ nh thá»±c pháº©m</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Hiá»‡n nay trÃªn thá»‹ trÆ°á»ng nhá»±a trao Ä‘á»•i Lanxess lÃ  thÆ°Æ¡ng hiá»‡u hÃ ng Ä‘áº§u vá» cÃ´ng nghá»‡ sáº£n xuáº¥t háº¡t Ä‘á»u (Monoplus) vá»›i tá»‰ lá»‡ Ä‘á»“ng nháº¥t cao.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">LÆ°u lÆ°á»£ng xá»­ lÃ½ cao vÃ  á»•n Ä‘á»‹nh</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Hiá»‡u quáº£ cá»§a quÃ¡ trÃ¬nh tÃ¡i sinh/hoÃ n nguyÃªn háº¡t nhá»±a trao Ä‘á»•i tá»‘t hÆ¡n</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '{"detail":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ea1t Cation S1567 Lanxess \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng, uy t\\u00edn ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 CO\\/CQ xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9.\\u00a0Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Hat%20cation%20C100E\\/hat-cation-C100E-bestwater.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"640\\" height=\\"480\\" \\/><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Hat%20Cation%20S1567\\/Hat-cation-S1567-Lanxess-1.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"441\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">1. \\u0110\\u1eb6C \\u0110I\\u1ec2M &amp; TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT.<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><strong>TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT C\\u01a0 B\\u1ea2N C\\u1ee6A H\\u1ea0T CATION S1567<\\/strong><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ec7 s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng nh\\u1ea5t: 1.1<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">K\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc h\\u1ea1t: 0.6 ( +\\/- 0.05 ) mm<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Dung tr\\u1ecdng: 810 g\\/l ( +\\/- 5% )<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">T\\u1ec9 tr\\u1ecdng: 1.28 g\\/ml<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Dung l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i: 2.0 eq\\/l ( Min )<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ho\\u00e1 ch\\u1ea5t ho\\u00e0n nguy\\u00ean: NaCl<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">N\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 ho\\u00e0n nguy\\u00ean: 8 ~ 12%<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kho\\u1ea3ng pH ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng: 5 ~ 8<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kho\\u1ea3ng pH ch\\u1ecbu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c: 0 ~ 14<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kho\\u1ea3ng nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9: -20 ~ 40 oC<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Th\\u1eddi gian l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef: 02 n\\u0103m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Hat%20Cation%20S1567\\/Mat-turoc-bao-Hat-cation-S1567-Lanxess-0.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong><strong>\\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG C\\u1ee6A H\\u1ea0T CATION S1567 LANXESS<\\/strong><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u01b0ng t\\u1ee5<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u00e0m m\\u1ec1m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc (kh\\u1eed kho\\u00e1ng)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong ng\\u00e0nh th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m, gi\\u1ea3i kh\\u00e1t: bia, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ecdt, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc tinh khi\\u1ebft,\\u2026.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Nh\\u1ef1a trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt ch\\u1ea5t h\\u00f2a tan kh\\u1ecfi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng. Do \\u0111\\u00f3, c\\u00e1c nh\\u00f3m ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c li\\u00ean k\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi h\\u1ea1t polymer. C\\u00e1c polyme ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng n\\u00e0y h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 c\\u00e1c anion ho\\u1eb7c cation \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t t\\u1eeb ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t kh\\u00e1c th\\u1ea3i ra.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc l\\u00e0 l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t cho c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i nh\\u1ef1a trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion. Trong h\\u1ed9 gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh, c\\u00e1c \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong s\\u1ed1 nh\\u1eefng th\\u1ee9 kh\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ec3\\u00a0l\\u00e0m m\\u1ec1m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. H\\u1ea1t trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion cation S1567 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o r\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1c ion canxi g\\u00e2y ra \\u0111\\u1ed9 c\\u1ee9ng c\\u1ee7a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thay th\\u1ebf b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1c ion natri.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ea1t cation S1567 c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 nh\\u01b0 trong ph\\u00e1t \\u0111i\\u1ec7n. \\u1ede \\u0111\\u00f3, h\\u1ea1t cation Lewatit S1567 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea5p h\\u01a1i n\\u1ed3i h\\u01a1i c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 tinh khi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u00e1nh hi\\u1ec7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0103n m\\u00f2n. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y n\\u00e2ng cao hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3, \\u0111\\u1ed9 tin c\\u1eady v\\u00e0 tu\\u1ed5i th\\u1ecd c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y \\u0111i\\u1ec7n.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Trong vi\\u1ec7c l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0v\\u00e0 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m, vi\\u1ec7c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9c h\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 quan tr\\u1ecdng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1c l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng kh\\u00e1c c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1ef1a trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion bao g\\u1ed3m s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ea5t b\\u00e1n d\\u1eabn, c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed, xi m\\u1ea1 (ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd c\\u00e1c kim lo\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0 v\\u00e0ng, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, niken ho\\u1eb7c coban trong hydrometalurgy), x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc d\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ea9m, y t\\u1ebf, x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc cho ng\\u00e0nh ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m v\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ea3i kh\\u00e1t. Trong s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t tinh th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng xi-r\\u00f4, S1567 c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng l\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng m\\u00eda n\\u00e2u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u00e0nh s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u1eafng v\\u00e0 v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o m\\u00f9i v\\u1ecb c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Nh\\u1ef1a trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ion S1567 c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t x\\u00fac t\\u00e1c c\\u00f3 t\\u00ednh ph\\u1ea3n \\u1ee9ng r\\u1ea5t quan tr\\u1ecdng \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ea3n \\u1ee9ng h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. CH\\u00cdNH S\\u00c1CH B\\u00c1N H\\u00c0NG C\\u1ee6A GMCVINA<\\/strong><br \\/><br \\/><strong>GMCWATER.COM\\u00a0<\\/strong>t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u va\\u0300 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00e2m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u201cLan t\\u1ecfa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng\\u201d th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch sau::<br \\/><br \\/><strong>GI\\u00c1 T\\u1eacN G\\u1ed0C:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA l\\u00e0 nha\\u0300 nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u, ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng t\\u01b0\\u0300 ca\\u0301c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u00ea\\u0323u l\\u01a1\\u0301n \\u0111\\u00ea\\u0301n t\\u01b0\\u0300 Nh\\u1eadt, H\\u00e0n, EU, M\\u1ef9 n\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M M\\u01a0\\u0301I 100%:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA ch\\u1ec9 b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng m\\u1edbi 100% c\\u00f2n nguy\\u00ean \\u0111ai nguy\\u00ean ki\\u1ec7n<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M CH\\u00cdNH H\\u00c3NG:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA s\\u1ebd g\\u1eedi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng xem tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn CO (Xu\\u1ea5t X\\u1ee9) + CQ (Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng), s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u00e1i\\/ c\\u0169 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 2 lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1n 10 l\\u1ea7n gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb mua h\\u00e0ng n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng nh\\u00e1i\\/ h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169 k\\u00e9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG L\\u00c0 S\\u1ed0 1:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb7t nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng l\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng mua thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1i\\u00a0gmcwater.com\\u00a0ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee9c chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd<br \\/><br \\/><strong>D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 T\\u1ed0T NH\\u1ea4T:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n 24\\/24 trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh mua v\\u00e0 sau mua. B\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 khi n\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng g\\u1eb7p v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong th\\u1eddi gian nhanh nh\\u1ea5t.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH D\\u00c0I H\\u1ea0N:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ngo\\u00e0i ph\\u1ea7n b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u00e3ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh ri\\u00eang t\\u1eeb ph\\u00eda GMC VINA theo ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">LI\\u00caN H\\u1ec6:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC 