(198, 'CÃ¡t Mangan', NULL, NULL, '<ul style="font-family: &quot;;">\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">CÃ¡t mangan Ä‘Æ°á»£c sá»­ dá»¥ng Ä‘á»ƒ lá»c nÆ°á»›c giáº¿ng khoan, khá»­ mÃ¹i nÆ°á»›c nhiá»…m Sáº¯t, nhiá»…m Mangan, Hydrogen sulfide, Asen, khá»­ mÃ¹i tanh báº±ng cÃ¡ch oxy hÃ³a trá»±c tiáº¿p qua tiáº¿p xÃºc vá»›i bá» máº·t cÃ¡t, káº¿t tá»§a vÃ  kháº£ nÄƒng lá»c cá»§a táº§ng háº¡t.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">XÃºc tÃ¡c quÃ¡ trÃ¬nh khá»­ sáº¯t (Fe &lt; 35 mg/l), khá»­ cÃ¡c cháº¥t phÃ³ng xáº¡.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Giáº£m hÃ m lÆ°á»£ng nitrogen (nitrit, nitrat, amÃ´ni), photphat (20-50% tÃ¹y theo tá»‘c Ä‘á»™ lá»c tá»« 4-7 m/giá»), khá»­ Flo trong nÆ°á»›c.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">PH nÆ°á»›c Ä‘áº§u vÃ o &gt;= 7,0, tháº¿ oxy hÃ³a khá»­ &gt; 700mV (Ä‘á»‘i vá»›i yÃªu cáº§u khá»­ mangan).</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Fe &lt; 30 mg/l; Mn &lt; 5mg/l.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">CÃ¡t mangan khÃ´ng cáº§n tÃ¡i sinh. Sau má»™t thá»i gian sá»­ dá»¥ng khoáº£ng 2 nÄƒm (tÃ¹y theo cháº¥t lÆ°á»£ng nÆ°á»›c nguá»“n) cáº§n thay tháº¿ hoáº·c hoáº¡t hÃ³a báº±ngÂ dung dá»‹ch KMnO4.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '{"detail":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i\\u00a0C\\u00e1t Mangan \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng, uy t\\u00edn ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 CO\\/CQ xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9.\\u00a0Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img style=\\"undefined\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Cat%20Mangan\\/Cat-mangan.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"725\\" height=\\"725\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">1. \\u0110\\u1eb6C \\u0110I\\u1ec2M &amp; TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT.<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">KH\\u1ea2 N\\u0102NG \\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG C\\u1ee6A C\\u00c1T MANGAN<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t mangan \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan, kh\\u1eed m\\u00f9i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m S\\u1eaft, nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan, Hydrogen sulfide, Asen, kh\\u1eed m\\u00f9i tanh b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch oxy h\\u00f3a tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp qua ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t c\\u00e1t, k\\u1ebft t\\u1ee7a v\\u00e0 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng l\\u1ecdc c\\u1ee7a t\\u1ea7ng h\\u1ea1t. V\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m th\\u00ec vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1t mangan r\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 trong vi\\u1ec7c lo\\u1ea1i kh\\u1eed c\\u00e1c kim lo\\u1ea1i n\\u1eb7ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, k\\u1ebdm, cr\\u00f4m, niken, Asen.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">X\\u00fac t\\u00e1c qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u1eed s\\u1eaft (Fe &lt; 35 mg\\/l), kh\\u1eed c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t ph\\u00f3ng x\\u1ea1.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Gi\\u1ea3m h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nitrogen (nitrit, nitrat, am\\u00f4ni), photphat (20-50% t\\u00f9y theo t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 l\\u1ecdc t\\u1eeb 4-7 m\\/gi\\u1edd), kh\\u1eed Flo trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Gi\\u1ea3m h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1 c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edb c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Mangan v\\u00e0 S\\u1eaft \\u1edf m\\u1ee9c cao g\\u1ea5p 3 \\u2013 5 l\\u1ea7n cho ph\\u00e9p.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img style=\\"undefined\\" src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Cat%20Mangan\\/Bao-cat-mangan-loai-25kg---Viet-Nam.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"626\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\u01afU \\u0110I\\u1ec2M C\\u1ee6A C\\u00c1T MANGAN<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">T\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 an to\\u00e0n cho ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sau x\\u1eed l\\u00fd<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">V\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n, \\u0111\\u01b0a tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c b\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc \\u0111ang s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i c\\u1ea5u tr\\u00fac b\\u1ec3<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc r\\u1eeda l\\u1ecdc\\u00a0th\\u1ea5p h\\u01a1n c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u kh\\u00e1c. Kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n s\\u1ee5c gi\\u00f3<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb \\u0111i k\\u00e8m nh\\u01b0 b\\u00ecnh pha h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t, b\\u01a1m \\u0111\\u1ecbnh l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00f3 tu\\u1ed5i th\\u1ecd cao nh\\u1edd kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ch\\u1ed1ng m\\u00e0i m\\u00f2n l\\u1edbn<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n t\\u00e1i sinh \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 b\\u1eb1ng dung d\\u1ecbch KMnO4 nh\\u01b0 Manganese green sand<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ea5p h\\u01a1n nhi\\u1ec1u so v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u nh\\u1eadp ngo\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0 h\\u1ea1t Pyrolox,\\u00a0Birm\\u00a0hay Manganese green sand<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. CH\\u00cdNH S\\u00c1CH B\\u00c1N H\\u00c0NG C\\u1ee6A GMCVINA<\\/strong><br \\/><br \\/><strong>GMCWATER.COM\\u00a0<\\/strong>t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u va\\u0300 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00e2m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u201cLan t\\u1ecfa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng\\u201d th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch sau::<br \\/><br \\/><strong>GI\\u00c1 T\\u1eacN G\\u1ed0C:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA l\\u00e0 nha\\u0300 nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u, ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng t\\u01b0\\u0300 ca\\u0301c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u00ea\\u0323u l\\u01a1\\u0301n \\u0111\\u00ea\\u0301n t\\u01b0\\u0300 Nh\\u1eadt, H\\u00e0n, EU, M\\u1ef9 n\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M M\\u01a0\\u0301I 100%:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA ch\\u1ec9 b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng m\\u1edbi 100% c\\u00f2n nguy\\u00ean \\u0111ai nguy\\u00ean ki\\u1ec7n<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M CH\\u00cdNH H\\u00c3NG:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA s\\u1ebd g\\u1eedi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng xem tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn CO (Xu\\u1ea5t X\\u1ee9) + CQ (Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng), s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u00e1i\\/ c\\u0169 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 2 lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1n 10 l\\u1ea7n gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb mua h\\u00e0ng n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng nh\\u00e1i\\/ h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169 k\\u00e9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG L\\u00c0 S\\u1ed0 1:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb7t nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng l\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng mua thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1i\\u00a0gmcwater.com\\u00a0ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee9c chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd<br \\/><br \\/><strong>D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 T\\u1ed0T NH\\u1ea4T:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n 24\\/24 trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh mua v\\u00e0 sau mua. B\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 khi n\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng g\\u1eb7p v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong th\\u1eddi gian nhanh nh\\u1ea5t.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH D\\u00c0I H\\u1ea0N:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ngo\\u00e0i ph\\u1ea7n b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u00e3ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh ri\\u00eang t\\u1eeb ph\\u00eda GMC VINA theo ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">LI\\u00caN H\\u1ec6:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">MST: 0107998239 do S\\u1edf K\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i c\\u1ea5p ng\\u00e0y 20\\/09\\/2017<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-fam