helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea1ng: d\\u1ea1ng h\\u1ea1t, m\\u00e0u \\u0111en, nhi\\u1ec1u g\\u00f3c c\\u1ea1nh<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">K\\u00edch c\\u1ee1 h\\u1ea1t: 0,7 \\u2013 3,15 mm<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac: 875 m2\\/g<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1ed1 iodine: t\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ec3u 700<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m: &lt; 2%<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ec7 s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng nh\\u1ea5t: 1.8<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">T\\u1ec9 tr\\u1ecdng: 290kg\\/m3<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">PH: Alkaline<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng: 2 \\u2013 6 gpm\\/cu.ft (t\\u00f9y theo ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Quy c\\u00e1ch: 12,5 kg\\/bao (t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng kho\\u1ea3ng 43L)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Than%20Norit%20Ha%20Lan\\/Than-hoat-tinh-Norit-PK1-3-1.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">VAI TR\\u00d2 C\\u1ee6A THAN HO\\u1ea0T T\\u00cdNH NORIT<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf m\\u00f9i, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Kh\\u1eed m\\u00e0u;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1;<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5 nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9c h\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0: Chlorine; C\\u1eb7n th\\u00f4; H\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1; M\\u00f9i h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t; Ph\\u00e2n b\\u00f3n, thu\\u1ed1c tr\\u1eeb s\\u00e2u; TCE (Trichloroethylene); B\\u1ed9t gi\\u1eb7t; EDB (Ethylene dibromide); Chloramines; THM (Trihalomethanes); V\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t kh\\u00e1c, \\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u1ee8ng d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1ed1t cho x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng, y t\\u1ebf, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t d\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ea9m, linh ki\\u1ec7n \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Than%20Norit%20Ha%20Lan\\/Than-hoat-tinh-Norit-PK1-3-2.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"800\\" height=\\"600\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. CH\\u00cdNH S\\u00c1CH B\\u00c1N H\\u00c0NG C\\u1ee6A GMCVINA<\\/strong><br \\/><br \\/><strong>GMCWATER.COM\\u00a0<\\/strong>t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u va\\u0300 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00e2m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u201cLan t\\u1ecfa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng\\u201d th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch sau::<br \\/><br \\/><strong>GI\\u00c1 T\\u1eacN G\\u1ed0C:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA l\\u00e0 nha\\u0300 nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u, ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng t\\u01b0\\u0300 ca\\u0301c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u00ea\\u0323u l\\u01a1\\u0301n \\u0111\\u00ea\\u0301n t\\u01b0\\u0300 Nh\\u1eadt, H\\u00e0n, EU, M\\u1ef9 n\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M M\\u01a0\\u0301I 100%:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA ch\\u1ec9 b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng m\\u1edbi 100% c\\u00f2n nguy\\u00ean \\u0111ai nguy\\u00ean ki\\u1ec7n<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M CH\\u00cdNH H\\u00c3NG:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA s\\u1ebd g\\u1eedi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng xem tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn CO (Xu\\u1ea5t X\\u1ee9) + CQ (Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng), s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u00e1i\\/ c\\u0169 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 2 lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1n 10 l\\u1ea7n gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb mua h\\u00e0ng n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng nh\\u00e1i\\/ h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169 k\\u00e9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG L\\u00c0 S\\u1ed0 1:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb7t nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng l\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng mua thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1i\\u00a0gmcwater.com\\u00a0ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee9c chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd<br \\/><br \\/><strong>D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 T\\u1ed0T NH\\u1ea4T:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n 24\\/24 trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh mua v\\u00e0 sau mua. B\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 khi n\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng g\\u1eb7p v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong th\\u1eddi gian nhanh nh\\u1ea5t.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH D\\u00c0I H\\u1ea0N:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ngo\\u00e0i ph\\u1ea7n b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u00e3ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh ri\\u00eang t\\u1eeb ph\\u00eda GMC VINA theo ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">LI\\u00caN H\\u1ec6:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">MST: 0107998239 do S\\u1edf K\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i c\\u1ea5p ng\\u00e0y 20\\/09\\/2017<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh: S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VPGD: T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VPGD chi nh\\u00e1nh TP. HCM\\u00a0: s\\u1ed1\\u00a092\\/20B\\/20\\/17 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Ph\\u1ea1m H\\u00f9ng, Ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng 4, Qu\\u1eadn 8, TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"tel:02466 835383\\"><span>02466 835383<\\/span><\\/a>\\u00a0- \\u00a0Fax:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: tran