(202, 'CÃ¡t tháº¡ch anh', NULL, NULL, '<ul style="font-family: &quot;;">\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Vai trÃ²: giá»¯ láº¡i cÃ¡c cháº¥t lÆ¡ lá»­ng, phÃ¹ du, phÃ¹ sa, xÃ¡c Ä‘á»™ng thá»±c váº­tâ€¦ khÃ´ng káº¿t tá»§a trong nÆ°á»›c</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Äáº·c Ä‘iá»ƒm: dáº¡ng háº¡t, Ä‘á»u, nhiá»u gÃ³c cáº¡nh</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">MÃ u sáº¯c: tráº¯ng ngÃ , vÃ ng nÃ¢u</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">KÃ­ch thÆ°á»›c: 0,4 â€“ 0,8 mm, 0,7 â€“ 1,2mm, 1 â€“ 2mm.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Quy cÃ¡ch: 40kg/bao</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Tá»· trá»ng: 1.400 kg/m3 â€“ 1,4kg/lÃ­t</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '{"detail":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng, uy t\\u00edn ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 CO\\/CQ xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9.\\u00a0Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Cat%20thach%20anh\\/Cat-thach-anh-kich-co-1-2mm.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"711\\" height=\\"533\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">1. \\u0110\\u1eb6C \\u0110I\\u1ec2M &amp; TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT.<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">VAI TR\\u00d2 C\\u1ee6A C\\u00c1T TH\\u1ea0CH ANH TRONG H\\u1ec6 TH\\u1ed0NG<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh d\\u00f9ng trong l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9 t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00e1 th\\u1ea1ch anh, l\\u00e0 lo\\u1ea1i v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u c\\u00f3 k\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u1ecf, g\\u00f3c c\\u1ea1nh h\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ec1u v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec1u g\\u00f3c c\\u1ea1nh c\\u00f3 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng l\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng, ph\\u00f9 du, ph\\u00f9 sa, x\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng th\\u1ef1c v\\u1eadt\\u2026 kh\\u00f4ng k\\u1ebft t\\u1ee7a trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t, ch\\u1ec9 cho n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ea1ch \\u0111i qua.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh l\\u1ecdc, tr\\u00ean b\\u00ean m\\u1eb7t c\\u00e1t s\\u1ebd xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c l\\u1ed7, tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c l\\u1ed7 n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 Fe(OH)3, khi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111i qua n\\u00f3 s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 asen, tr\\u00e1nh v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m asen.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng l\\u1ea1i nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1ea7n, khi b\\u1ecb b\\u1ea9n v\\u00e0 l\\u1eafng c\\u1eb7n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u00f9ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc r\\u1eeda s\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 t\\u00e1i s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1ea7n m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng l\\u00e0m b\\u1ea9n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1edbi s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe. Vi\\u1ec7c n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng van \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n nguy\\u00ean li\\u1ec7u c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh t\\u1ea1i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ed1i d\\u1ed3i d\\u00e0o, khai th\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n v\\u00e0 gi\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea3i ch\\u0103ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u1ede c\\u00e1c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi, c\\u00e1t l\\u1ecdc th\\u1ea1ch anh d\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, x\\u1eed l\\u00fd c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nhi\\u1ec5m Asen v\\u00e0 gi\\u00fap lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ebfn 70% t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT C\\u1ee6A C\\u00c1T TH\\u1ea0CH ANH<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m: d\\u1ea1ng h\\u1ea1t, \\u0111\\u1ec1u, nhi\\u1ec1u g\\u00f3c c\\u1ea1nh<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">M\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc: tr\\u1eafng ng\\u00e0, v\\u00e0ng n\\u00e2u<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">K\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc: 0,4 \\u2013 0,8 mm, 0,7 \\u2013 1,2mm, 1 \\u2013 2mm, 1.5-2.5mm\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Quy c\\u00e1ch: 40kg\\/bao<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">T\\u1ef7 tr\\u1ecdng: 1.400 kg\\/m3 \\u2013 1,4kg\\/l\\u00edt<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9: Vi\\u1ec7t Nam<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh:C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh c\\u00f3 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n ch\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 Silic dioxit (SiO2), b\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f2n ch\\u1ee9a m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 nguy\\u00ean t\\u1ed1 h\\u00f3a h\\u1ecdc kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0: NaCl, CO2 ,H2O , CaCO3,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Cat%20thach%20anh\\/Bao-cat-thach-anh.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"750\\" height=\\"814\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\u01afU \\u0110I\\u1ec2M C\\u1ee6A C\\u00c1T TH\\u1ea0CH ANH<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh c\\u00f3 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n t\\u1ef7 l\\u1ec7 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n h\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea5u t\\u1ea1o kh\\u00f4ng gi\\u1ed1ng c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c kh\\u00e1c m\\u1eb7c d\\u00f9 gi\\u1ed1ng c\\u00e1t v\\u00e0ng hay d\\u00f9ng trong x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1ec1 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u00ec \\u01b0u vi\\u1ec7t h\\u01a1n r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u, gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i c\\u1eb7n b\\u1ea9n t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n, kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ecb t\\u1eafc nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1t v\\u00e0ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh th\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ee7 th\\u1eddi gian ch\\u1ea3y qua c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea7ng v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m quan tr\\u1ecdng l\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng ho\\u00e0 tan trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, kh\\u00f4ng sinh ra c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ed9c h\\u1ea1i. T\\u00ednh b\\u1ecb b\\u00e0o m\\u00f2n trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u00edt h\\u01a1n do ngu\\u1ed3n g\\u1ed1c xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh l\\u00e0 t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00e1 th\\u1ea1ch anh. C\\u1ea5u t\\u1ea1o c\\u00e1c ph\\u00e2n t\\u1eed c\\u1ee7a lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1t n\\u00e0y c\\u0169ng r\\u1ea5t b\\u1ec1n b\\u1ec9 n\\u00ean khi cho n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111i qua, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m ho\\u1eb7c d\\u00ednh c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i ph\\u00e2n t\\u1eed c\\u00f3 h\\u1ea1i (n\\u1ebfu c\\u00f3) trong lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1t n\\u00e0y. Do v\\u1eady n\\u00ean khi l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc h\\u1ebft l\\u00e0 an to\\u00e0n h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1t kh\\u00e1c.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">T\\u00ednh \\u201cm\\u1ec1m\\u201d c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 \\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u1edbn. C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh c\\u00f3 k\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u1ecf n\\u00ean c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ec3 x\\u00e2y hay c\\u1ed9t l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 \\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt n\\u1ebfu so s\\u00e1nh v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea5m l\\u1ecdc, l\\u01b0\\u1edbi l\\u1ecdc hay b\\u00f9i nh\\u00f9i\\u2026 V\\u1eadn chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3i c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\u1ee8NG D\\u1ee4NG C\\u1ee6A C\\u00c1T TH\\u1ea0CH ANH<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh n\\u00f3i ri\\u00eang v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1t n\\u00f3i chung l\\u00e0 v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 thi\\u1ebfu \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u00f3 nhu c\\u1ea7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan. N\\u00f3 \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch kinh t\\u1ebf r\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn v\\u00e0 v\\u00f4 c\\u00f9ng hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3. Trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc gi\\u1ebfng khoan c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n th\\u00ec c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh mu\\u1ed1n ph\\u00e1t huy s\\u1ee9c m\\u1ea1nh t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a, n\\u00f3 c\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 lo\\u1ea1i v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0: than ho\\u1ea1t t\\u00ednh, c\\u00e1t mangan, h\\u1ea1t birm\\u2026 C\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ed5 tr\\u00ean v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ee1 l\\u00e0 s\\u1ecfi l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea5p, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc tinh khi\\u1ebft, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc sinh ho\\u1ea1t cho h\\u1ed9 gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngo\\u00e0i ra r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u00e1c c\\u0169ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh nh\\u01b0: x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng, \\u0111\\u1ed5 b\\u00ea t\\u00f4ng, ch\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5m, c\\u00e1c m\\u00e1y c\\u1eaft plasma mini,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u00e0 1 trong c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng, l\\u00e1t g\\u1ea1ch, v\\u1ec9 h\\u00e8, tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e2y\\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong ng\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p phun s\\u01a1n, c\\u1eaft k\\u00ednh, \\u0111\\u00fac Porter, luy\\u1ec7n kim \\u2026<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">C\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u00f9ng trong phong th\\u1ee7y (n\\u1ebfu c\\u00e1c kh\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e1 th\\u1ea1ch anh l\\u1edbn, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 h\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i phong th\\u1ee7y y\\u00eau th\\u00edch).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>2. CH\\u00cdNH S\\u00c1CH B\\u00c1N H\\u00c0NG C\\u1ee6A GMCVINA<\\/strong><br \\/><br \\/><strong>GMCWATER.COM\\u00a0<\\/strong>t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u va\\u0300 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00e2m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u201cLan t\\u1ecfa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng\\u201d th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch sau::<br \\/><br \\/><strong>GI\\u00c1 T\\u1eacN G\\u1ed0C:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA l\\u00e0 nha\\u0300 nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u, ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng t\\u01b0\\u0300 ca\\u0301c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u00ea\\u0323u l\\u01a1\\u0301n \\u0111\\u00ea\\u0301n t\\u01b0\\u0300 Nh\\u1eadt, H\\u00e0n, EU, M\\u1ef9 n\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M M\\u01a0\\u0301I 100%:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA ch\\u1ec9 b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng m\\u1edbi 100% c\\u00f2n nguy\\u00ean \\u0111ai nguy\\u00ean ki\\u1ec7n<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M CH\\u00cdNH H\\u00c3NG:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA s\\u1ebd g\\u1eedi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng xem tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn CO (Xu\\u1ea5t X\\u1ee9) + CQ (Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng), s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u00e1i\\/ c\\u0169 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 2 lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1n 10 l\\u1ea7n gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb mua h\\u00e0ng n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng nh\\u00e1i\\/ h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169 k\\u00e9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG L\\u00c0 S\\u1ed0 1:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb7t nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng l\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng mua thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1i\\u00a0gmcwater.com\\u00a0ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee9c chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd<br \\/><br \\/><strong>D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 T\\u1ed0T NH\\u1ea4T:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n 24\\/24 trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh mua v\\u00e0 sau mua. B\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 khi n\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng g\\u1eb7p v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong th\\u1eddi gian nhanh nh\\u1ea5t.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH D\\u00c0I H\\u1ea0N:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ngo\\u00e0i ph\\u1ea7n b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh theo h\\u00e3ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh ri\\u00eang t\\u1eeb ph\\u00eda GMC VINA theo ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">LI\\u00caN H\\u1ec6:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">C\\u00d4NG TY CP THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca &amp;C\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 M\\u00d4I TR\\u01af\\u1edcNG GMC VINA<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">MST: 0107998239 do S\\u1edf K\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i c\\u1ea5p ng\\u00e0y 20\\/09\\/2017<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh: S\\u1ed1 27, ng\\u00f5 28\\/90\\/19 Ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u1ea1i Linh, P.Trung V\\u0103n, Q.Nam T\\u1eeb Li\\u00eam,H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VPGD: T\\u1ea7ng 2, T\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 Pvv Vinapharm, s\\u1ed1 60B Nguy\\u1ec5n Huy T\\u01b0\\u1edfng, Q. Thanh Xu\\u00e2n, TP. H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i.<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">VPGD chi nh\\u00e1nh TP. HCM\\u00a0: s\\u1ed1\\u00a092\\/20B\\/20\\/17 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Ph\\u1ea1m H\\u00f9ng, Ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng 4, Qu\\u1eadn 8, TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"tel:02466 835383\\"><span>02466 835383<\\/span><\\/a>\\u00a0- \\u00a0Fax:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"tel:02466.835383\\"><span>02466.835383<\\/span><\\/a><\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Hotline: 0989980178<\\/span><br style=\\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\\" \\/><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">Email:\\u00a0<a style=\\"color: #337ab7; font-size: 15px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;\\" href=\\"mailto:info@gmcvina.com\\"><span>info@gmcvina.com<\\/span><\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>","specification":"","media":""}', 'CÃ¡t tháº¡ch anh', 'CÃ¡t tháº¡ch anh', 'CÃ¡t tháº¡ch anh', 0, 691, 2, '2020-04-10 10:27:46', '2020-04-10 10:27:46'),
(203, 'Háº¡t xá»‘p Xifo', NULL, NULL, '<ul style="font-family: &quot;;">\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Äáº·c Ä‘iá»ƒm: dáº¡ng háº¡t hÃ¬nh cáº§u, mÃ u tráº¯ng, nháº¹ hÆ¡n nÆ°á»›c nÃªn cÃ²n Ä‘Æ°á»£c gá»i lÃ  háº¡t lá»c ná»•i xifo</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">KÃ­ch thÆ°á»›c: loáº¡i nhá» 2-3mm, loáº¡i lá»›n 3-5mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Diá»‡n tÃ­ch bá» máº·t tiáº¿p xÃºc: 1.150 m2/m3 (háº¡t 2-3mm); 600 m2/m3 (háº¡t 3-5mm)</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Lá»c sáº¯t vÃ  mangan theo hÃ¬nh thá»©c háº¥p phá»¥</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Lá»c cáº·n lÆ¡ lá»­ng, phÃ¹ sa trong nÆ°á»›c</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">LÃ m giÃ¡ thá»ƒ sinh há»c xá»­ lÃ½ nÆ°á»›c tháº£i</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '{"detail":"<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">GMC VINA chuy\\u00ean ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ea1t x\\u1ed1p Xifo \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng, uy t\\u00edn ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 CO\\/CQ xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9.\\u00a0Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Hat%20xop%20Xifo\\/Hat-xop-Xifo-1.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"640\\" height=\\"640\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\">I. \\u0110\\u1eb6C \\u0110I\\u1ec2M &amp; TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT.<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>TH\\u00d4NG S\\u1ed0 K\\u1ef8 THU\\u1eacT C\\u1ee6A H\\u1ea0T X\\u1ed0P XIFO<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/div>\\r\\n<ul style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m: d\\u1ea1ng h\\u1ea1t h\\u00ecnh c\\u1ea7u, m\\u00e0u tr\\u1eafng, nh\\u1eb9 h\\u01a1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc n\\u00ean c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 h\\u1ea1t l\\u1ecdc n\\u1ed5i xifo<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n: polystyrene, g\\u1ed1c styrofor, PS, PS2<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">K\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc: lo\\u1ea1i nh\\u1ecf 2-3mm, lo\\u1ea1i l\\u1edbn 3-5mm<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac: 1.150 m2\\/m3 (h\\u1ea1t 2-3mm); 600 m2\\/m3 (h\\u1ea1t 3-5mm)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ea1n d\\u00f9ng: t\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ec3u 2 n\\u0103m, \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 r\\u1eeda c\\u1eb7n b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch s\\u1ee5c d\\u00f2ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">\\u0110\\u00f3ng bao: 1 m3 (chu\\u1ea9n)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9: Vi\\u1ec7t Nam<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">VAI TR\\u00d2 C\\u1ee6A H\\u1ea0T X\\u1ed0P XIFO<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">H\\u1ea1t x\\u1ed1p xifo c\\u00f3 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng l\\u1ecdc s\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 mangan theo h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c h\\u1ea5p ph\\u1ee5. N\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd ch\\u1ea3y t\\u1eeb d\\u01b0\\u1edbi l\\u00ean, len l\\u1ecfi v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c khe c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ea1t x\\u1ed1p v\\u00e0 s\\u1eaft, mangan b\\u1ecb gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ea1t x\\u1ed1p<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u1ecdc c\\u1eb7n l\\u01a1 l\\u1eedng, ph\\u00f9 sa trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u00e0m gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 sinh h\\u1ecdc\\u00a0x\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><img src=\\"\\/app\\/webroot\\/js\\/admin\\/upload_image\\/image\\/Vat%20lieu%20loc\\/Hat%20xop%20Xifo\\/Hat-xop-Xifo-3.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"512\\" height=\\"384\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\">H\\u01af\\u1edaNG D\\u1eaaN S\\u1eec D\\u1ee4NG H\\u1ea0T X\\u1ed0P XIFO<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"font-family: &quot;;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>1. X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ea7m<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1eaft cao 15 \\u2013 40mg\\/l: \\u0110\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng th\\u00e1p oxy h\\u00f3a ho\\u1eb7c\\u00a0ejector tr\\u1ed9n kh\\u00ed\\u00a0\\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea5y th\\u00eam oxy; n\\u1ebfu c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u00e2m h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u00e2ng pH, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh l\\u1ecdc qua 2 c\\u00f4ng \\u0111o\\u1ea1n: l\\u1ecdc th\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng h\\u1ea1t x\\u1ed1p xifo v\\u00e0 l\\u1ecdc tinh b\\u1eb1ng c\\u1ed9t l\\u1ecdc\\u00a0c\\u00e1t th\\u1ea1ch anh.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1eaft nh\\u1ecf h\\u01a1n 15 mg\\/l: \\u0110\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng th\\u00e1p oxy h\\u00f3a ho\\u1eb7c ejector \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea5y th\\u00eam oxy; n\\u1ebfu c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u00e2m h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u00e2ng pH, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh l\\u1ecdc qua 2 c\\u00f4ng \\u0111o\\u1ea1n nh\\u01b0 tr\\u00ean (Fe = 10 \\u2013 15mg\\/l), ho\\u1eb7c ch\\u1ec9 c\\u1ea7n l\\u1ecdc qua 1 c\\u00f4ng \\u0111o\\u1ea1n ( Fe &lt; 10mg\\/l).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a h\\u00e0m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng mangan &lt; 5mg\\/l: Sau m\\u1ed9t th\\u1eddi gian s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kho\\u1ea3ng 2 tu\\u1ea7n \\u2013 1 th\\u00e1ng, khi b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t h\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u00e3 ph\\u1ee7 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1edbp oxit s\\u1eaft m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng n\\u00e2u, ho\\u1eb7c oxit mangan m\\u00e0u n\\u00e2u \\u0111en, l\\u00fac \\u0111\\u00f3 h\\u1ea1t tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u x\\u00fac t\\u00e1c qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh oxy h\\u00f3a s\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 mangan r\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3. Do v\\u1eady h\\u1ea1t c\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng l\\u00e2u c\\u00e0ng t\\u1ed1t.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>2. X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u1eb7t<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ee5c th\\u1ea5p (&lt; 100 NTU): s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u1ea1t l\\u1ecdc 2 \\u2013 3mm, \\u0111\\u1ed9 d\\u00e0y l\\u1edbp v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc 1m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ee5c 100 \\u2013 300 NTU: s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng 1,5 \\u2013 2mm, \\u0111\\u1ed9 d\\u00e0y 1m<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ee5c &gt; 300 NTU: kh\\u00f4ng khuy\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1o s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>3. X\\u1eed l\\u00fd n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i<\\/strong><\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">L\\u00e0 gi\\u00e1 th\\u1ec3 sinh h\\u1ecdc cho qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh x\\u1eed l\\u00fd hi\\u1ebfu kh\\u00ed, k\\u1ef5 kh\\u00ed b\\u1eb1ng vi sinh v\\u1eadt sinh tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng b\\u00e1m d\\u00ednh, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u1ea1t 3 \\u2013 5mm.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\"><strong>4. X\\u1ea3 r\\u1eeda<\\/strong><\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\\">Khi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc x\\u1ea5u \\u0111i c\\u1ea7n ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh r\\u1eeda l\\u1ecdc b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch x\\u1ea3 b\\u1ecf 1m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ph\\u00eda tr\\u00ean l\\u1edbp v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u (s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u00f4, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n b\\u01a1m r\\u1eeda l\\u1ecdc). Sau \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u1eb7p l\\u1ea1i chu tr\\u00ecnh l\\u1ecdc nh\\u01b0 c\\u0169.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\\"><strong>II. CH\\u00cdNH S\\u00c1CH B\\u00c1N H\\u00c0NG C\\u1ee6A GMCVINA<\\/strong><br \\/><br \\/><strong>GMCWATER.COM\\u00a0<\\/strong>t\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0o l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u va\\u0300 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u00e3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Qua nhi\\u00ea\\u0300u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c cung c\\u00e2\\u0301p ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho qu\\u00fd kh\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00e2m ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u201cLan t\\u1ecfa gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng\\u201d th\\u00f4ng qua nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch sau::<br \\/><br \\/><strong>GI\\u00c1 T\\u1eacN G\\u1ed0C:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA l\\u00e0 nha\\u0300 nh\\u00e2\\u0323p kh\\u00e2\\u0309u, ph\\u00e2n ph\\u00f4\\u0301i c\\u00e1c d\\u00f2ng sa\\u0309n ph\\u00e2\\u0309m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u00ednh h\\u00e3ng t\\u01b0\\u0300 ca\\u0301c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u00ea\\u0323u l\\u01a1\\u0301n \\u0111\\u00ea\\u0301n t\\u01b0\\u0300 Nh\\u1eadt, H\\u00e0n, EU, M\\u1ef9 n\\u00ean gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M M\\u01a0\\u0301I 100%:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA ch\\u1ec9 b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng m\\u1edbi 100% c\\u00f2n nguy\\u00ean \\u0111ai nguy\\u00ean ki\\u1ec7n<br \\/><br \\/><strong>S\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M CH\\u00cdNH H\\u00c3NG:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA s\\u1ebd g\\u1eedi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng xem tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn CO (Xu\\u1ea5t X\\u1ee9) + CQ (Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng), s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u00e1i\\/ c\\u0169 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 2 lo\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea5y ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ec1n 10 l\\u1ea7n gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb mua h\\u00e0ng n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng nh\\u00e1i\\/ h\\u00e0ng c\\u0169 k\\u00e9m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG L\\u00c0 S\\u1ed0 1:<\\/strong>\\u00a0GMC VINA lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eb7t nhu c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng l\\u00ean h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady khi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng mua thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u l\\u1ecdc n\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea1i\\u00a0gmcwater.com\\u00a0ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee9c chi ph\\u00ed h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd<br \\/><br \\/><strong>D\\u1ecaCH V\\u1ee4 T\\u1ed0T NH\\u1ea4T:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n 24\\/24 trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh mua v\\u00e0 sau mua. B\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 khi n\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng g\\u1eb7p v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i cam k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd x\\u1eed l\\u00fd trong th\\u1eddi gian nhanh nh\\u1ea5t.<br \\/><br \\/><strong>B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH D\\u00c0I H\\u1ea0N:<\\/stro